 </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Our results are our best advertisement. </span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">That is why our clients recommend us, come back to us, and highly appreciate us for results achievement.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWant to learn more about Our services here: <a href=\"http://rightonit1/seo-and-organic-search-ranking/\">SEO and organic search ranking</a> or  fill out the form below and we will contact You in 24 hours - depending on your timezone!\r\n\r\n[caldera_form id=\"CF566f1dffedc4e\"]','Why SEO is so important','','publish','closed','closed','','why-seo-is-so-important','','','2025-10-20 10:47:59','2025-10-20 07:47:59','',0,'http://www.wiseswans.com/2016/12/31/why-seo-is-so-important/',0,'post','',0),(1700,3,'2016-12-31 06:25:03','2016-12-31 06:25:03','<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"http://rightonit1/seo-and-organic-search-ranking/\">SEO </a>audit of a website is an effective way to boost organic search results and drive targeted traffic.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The website audit is needed if: </span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Current results of the website promotion do not satisfy and an expert review is needed. </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The website is new and needs to be optimized with regard to the plans for subsequent promotion.<a href=\"http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/th-1.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-1225 alignright\" src=\"http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/th-1.jpg\" alt=\"th (1)\" width=\"238\" height=\"178\" /></a></span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You promote the website using automated systems and you need primary optimization of the website. </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You want to hold an analysis of your competitors.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As a result of such analytical work you will get a full search audit with more than a hundred of recommendations on how to optimize your website for promotion. We will analyze your website on compliance with the requirements of search engines, will find errors that jeopardize promotion and reduce traffic conversion from search.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you need any additional analysis for your project, within the frameworks of SEO audit we are ready to do the following for an additional payment:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Estimating budget of the website  SEO promotion.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The prospects and forecast of the website promotion. </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Analyzing competitors under the given parameters. </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The promotion strategy.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ol>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>The service includes: </b></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</ol>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Internal audit of the website:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Indexation and server setting.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Webpages’ URL setting.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Setting critical for indexation files Sitemap, Robots.txt and others.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Recommendations for webpage code contents.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Recommendations for website navigation.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Webpages interlinking.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Checking whether all content is unique.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Recommendations for sections content.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Creating content for any possible landing page. </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Recommendations on how to enhance the content in general sections.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Filling meta tags.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">External audit of the website:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Analyzing current links.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Analyzing competitors in  Google organic search with regard to volume and quality of links.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Analyzing competitors with regard to the quantity and quality of requests in index. </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Analyzing competitors with regard to the content and its variety. </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Analyzing competitors with regard to behavioral factors. </span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ol>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>The result you get</b></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</ol>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Organic search improvement and traffic boost .</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Effective strategy of the website promotion.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Recommendations on how to eliminate errors made in course of the website promotions. </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Advice of SEO experts.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>               2. Price Quote for SEO services</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The pricing for SEO in San Diego is calculated based on hourly rate value and volume of labor costs of a SEO specialist. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Prior to entering into an agreement we will provide you with the contents of the SEO audit and the parameters with which we are going to work. To ensure the high quality of the audit we will need: </span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">access to the website statistics to estimate the traffic; </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">access to the accounts of link marketplaces (if you have any);</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">history of the website promotion.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nStill got questions? Not sure what services you need?\r\n\r\nCall us now, visit this page <a href=\"http://rightonit1/seo-and-organic-search-ranking/\">SEO</a> or fill out the webform below:\r\n\r\n[caldera_form id=\"CF566f1dffedc4e\"]','Pricing for SEO audit of website','','publish','closed','closed','','pricing-for-seo-audit-of-website','','','2025-10-20 10:55:10','2025-10-20 07:55:10','',0,'http://www.wiseswans.com/2016/12/31/pricing-for-seo-audit-of-website/',0,'post','',0),(1702,3,'2016-12-31 06:25:03','2016-12-31 06:25:03','<h2>Links for the website promotion</h2>\r\nWe, as well as the search engines, desire to see in the results only attractive websites of high quality and good usability, completely meeting users’ requirements, and filled with interesting and useful content.\r\n\r\nAnd unlike the search engines we are capable of turning such desires into reality. 80% of our work is concentrated on these factors. The rest 20% is left for working with the website links that are still considered a substantial parameter in website ranking, despite the opinion of the search engines.\r\n\r\nBacklink building is a very important part of <a href=\"http://rightonit1/2016/01/12/why-seo-is-so-important/\">SEO</a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There are several categories of external links:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Natural links</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, that can be gained for proper and interesting content, to which other users or websites’ administrators will be willing to refer, such as articles, photo or video content, blog or forum. Natural links are most valuable foe search engines. </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Permanent links</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> are bought on special link marketplaces, and if donor platforms were chosen wisely such links look like natural for the search engines. But there is a lot of restrictions so this part should be used very careful.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Links from social networks</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> (Facebook, G+ and others) </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">and quicklinks from Twitter </span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">– made an excellent showing when promoting in topics that need a large number of users to be involved (websites with video or audio content, blogs, information portals). Search engines pay more attention to them than earlier treating them as natural user links. They work quickly and smoothly, because the search engines have a special pool of quickbots that several times a day check social networks. For example, a complete indexation of Twitter links takes only six hours.  </span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThat\'s how Wise Swans Web Design company works:\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">First of all our efforts are concentrated on forming natural links. For this purpose we create ideas to develop your website, we give recommendations regarding content. If there is a need to buy links, we thoroughly select donors, setting the highest requirements. When selecting platforms we take into account its topic, traffic, correlation of inbound and outbound links, and PageRank, percentage of indexed pages, registration in various catalogs, overall <a href=\"http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/th-2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-1230\" src=\"http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/th-2.jpg\" alt=\"th (2)\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a>look of the website, content quantity. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We thoroughly select links for a new website to start promotion from high quality environment. This gives the website a chance to quickly get high positions in Google organic search where requirements to the links are tougher. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If the website has already been promoted it is important to get rid of low quality links history (if any) and to create new links. For this purpose we analyze the links, detect strong and weak spots, as, for example, unstable dynamics, incorrect anchors, donor does not correspond to the topic, etc. If we are not satisfied with the quality of links we replace them with new ones.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">On monthly basis we analyze and check indexation of links, track the state of donor platforms, write anchors. Once in every six months we hold deep and full analysis of links, and based on the results we actualize link strategy of the website.</span>\r\n\r\nIf you want to improve your organic search ranking by getting links - we can help you! It doesn\'t really matter that our SEO company has offices  in Miami, San Diego, San Francisco, Boston and Houston  - we can serve all states, no matter wherу you are located.','Links for the website promotion','','publish','closed','closed','','links-for-web-promotin','','','2025-10-20 10:54:52','2025-10-20 07:54:52','',0,'http://www.wiseswans.com/2016/12/31/links-for-web-promotin/',0,'post','',0),(1704,3,'2016-12-31 06:25:03','2016-12-31 06:25:03','<h2>SEO optimization of website structure</h2>\r\nA proper structure is 50% of the foundation for a successful website promotion. If the website structure is complicated, illogical and multilayer it is bad for both visitors and the search engines. But that\'s primary a web design issue. To aviod that - visit this page to know more about <a href=\"http://rightonit1/selling-management/\">Web Design usability impovement</a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A web crawler has limited time to go through your website and index it. Our task is to make this procedure effective to the greatest possible extent. That is why first of all we will recommend you introducing userfriendly and well planned containment tree.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We are against creating meaningless pages aimed only at distributing semantic kernel of search queries. In this regard we always come up with options allowing to add missing landing pages in the current website structure and make it look as logical as possible, or to change the website structure hitting requirements of the search engines and user’s logic at the same time. </span>\r\n<ol>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>How the structure is created</b></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</ol>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">First of all we analyze your business and appraise how the current structure can cover the semantic kernel, we <img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-1233\" src=\"http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/chart-edited-300x241.jpg\" alt=\"chart-edited\" width=\"300\" height=\"241\" />compare your website structure with the websites of your closest competitors. We divide the semantic kernel into logical groups based on its characteristics, for example, color, size, category of goods and others, then we find interceptions in these groups. This allows us to determine whether it is enough to add filters to the site or it is necessary to create separate sections for each group of characteristics. Therefore we get the optimized website structure created taking into account the users’ logic and the requirements of search engines.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The  good SEO website structure should:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">be hierarchical, ideally not more than three clicks from the home page;</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">cover the entire semantic kernel in the topic;</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">be logical, concise and userfriendly.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In addition to the navigation structure we recommend using also the following features with regard to the search engines’ requirements: proper addresses of pages, format of internal interlinking of the website, etc.</span>\r\n\r\nIf you need more information about our Web Design and SEO company in San Diego - visit our primary page <a href=\"http://rightonit1/seo-and-organic-search-ranking/\">SEO and organic search </a> or fill out the form below.\r\n\r\n[caldera_form id=\"CF566f1dffedc4e\"]','SEO optimization of website structure','','publish','closed','closed','','seo-optimization-of-website-structure','','','2025-10-20 10:54:33','2025-10-20 07:54:33','',0,'http://www.wiseswans.com/2016/12/31/seo-optimization-of-website-structure/',0,'post','',0),(1706,3,'2016-12-31 06:25:03','2016-12-31 06:25:03','<h2>Internal interlinking</h2>\r\nInternal interlinking is an important part of the SEO and organic search ranking which not only allows to offer additional services, goods or content to the user, and thus to increase the average bill, but also helps to redistribute<a href=\"http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/th-3.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-1236\" src=\"http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/th-3-300x184.jpg\" alt=\"th (3)\" width=\"300\" height=\"184\" /></a> the weight in the website and improve behavioral factor.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A well organized interlinking provides an opportunity for the user to go from the page of certain level to the associated category of the same level. In other words when visiting a flypage of an e-commerce store the user should have an opportunity to check out accessories for this item or goods from the other related category.</span>\r\n\r\nThis is not that easy as it seems - so delegate this part to professionals - Wise Swans will help you on every step of SEO\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/seo-optimization-of-website-structure/\">SEO optimization of website structure</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/why-seo-is-so-important/\">Why SEO is so important</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://rightonit1/2016/01/12/links-for-web-promotin/\">Links for the website promotion</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/seo-and-organic-search-ranking/\">SEO and organic search ranking</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nStill got Questions? Feel free to Call US or ask a Question via webform below!\r\n\r\n[caldera_form id=\"CF566f1dffedc4e\"]','Internal interlinking','','publish','closed','closed','','internal-interlinking','','','2025-10-20 10:54:03','2025-10-20 07:54:03','',0,'http://www.wiseswans.com/2016/12/31/internal-interlinking/',0,'post','',0),(1708,3,'2016-12-31 06:25:03','2016-12-31 06:25:03','<h2>Strategy of website marketing</h2>\r\nA proper strategy in large part determines success and speed of the website seash marketing. To create a strategy we need to understand what goals and in what timeframes we are trying to meet. In other words SEO strategy is a plan for meeting a certain goal within a set timeframe.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The main goal for promoting the website in the search engines may be: gaining higher positions in the organic search results in a number of significant queries in six months or increasing the search traffic on 10 thousand visits in one year, as well as increasing in two times as many orders from the website in 9 months. It is crucial that the goals be attainable and be in line with the search engines reality and current condition of the website (that\'s why usability is so important). If the goal is formulated incorrectly this might be a waste of time and financial resources, and the result might be never achieved.   </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The strategy is created for each website individually and depends on numerous factors:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Type of the website.</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> An e-commerce store, a content project, a monobrand site and others – each will have its own marketing strategy. </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Topic of the resource. </span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To create the strategy one should understand: how competitive is the topic of the <a href=\"http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/web-marketing@2x.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-1239\" src=\"http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/web-marketing@2x-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"web-marketing@2x\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" /></a>website, what is the size of the search kernel, and is there any seasonal activity, etc.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Age of the website.</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> For example, it is impossible to promote a new website in popular competitive commercial queries.</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In addition it is important to take into account special features of different search engines. For example, at the initial stage Google may be in priority, though it is not the most popular in the Bing, but in Google the first results appear significantly quicker. </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Previous history of the website marketing and development. </span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For example, the website had been rebuilt and pages URLs have been changed, but redirection from old URL to new URL have not been set. This may have negative impact on the website position in the search results and the search traffic. With Wise Swans web design company in San Diego we know how to avoid that!</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Structure of the website.</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Whether it complies with the structure of the search query, whether significant changes are needed. </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Current content of the website .</span></i></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Geography.</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> It is useless to try promoting the website in geo dependent queries in a foreign state. Probably it is necessary to divide the website into different subdomains or different webpages for each website. </span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Taking into account that SEO is a complicated and deep work out of all factors that influence on ranking, our SEO Company will help you  choose the strategy for search promotion based on our hands-on experience. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We are able to write a lot of high quality content for your website, develop technical recommendations to have the web crawler go through all pages, we analyze your traffic, propose ways to increase conversion, place external high quality links , and analyze your competitors. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Depending on the current condition of your website we use different approaches for strategy creation.</span>\r\n\r\nDo you want to know more <a href=\"http://rightonit1/2016/01/12/why-seo-is-so-important/\">Why SEO is so important?</a>\r\n\r\nHave Questions?\r\n\r\nContact Us now\r\n\r\n[caldera_form id=\"CF566f1dffedc4e\"]','Strategy of website marketing','','publish','closed','closed','','strategy-of-website-marketing','','','2025-10-20 10:53:47','2025-10-20 07:53:47','',0,'http://www.wiseswans.com/2016/12/31/strategy-of-website-marketing/',0,'post','',0),(1710,3,'2016-12-31 06:25:03','2016-12-31 06:25:03','<h2>New website under development</h2>\r\n<strong><em> </em></strong>If you only plan or have just started to develop a website we recommend you involving SEO experts at the initial\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/SEO1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-1242\" src=\"http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/SEO1-300x180.jpg\" alt=\"SEO1\" width=\"300\" height=\"180\" /></a>stage of the web development. This will give you a huge advantage – you will get  already optimized website for search engines with correctly set CMS, correct URLs, optimal structure, and necessary amount of content posted in a right place, etc.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Usually 85%  of just-made websites need additional development to meet the  SEO requirements of the search engines which imply additional expenses. Web-developers create beautiful and good resources, but more often they don’t understand <a href=\"http://rightonit1/2016/01/12/seo-optimization-of-website-structure/\">SEO </a>at all. Our SEO specialists in San Diego will run a number of procedures and draft recommendations which are needed to be implemented in the website that the web crawlers started indexing it straight after launching.  </span>\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What 