elopment, it’s already possible to think over about its further promotion because otherwise there would be no any possibility to make it popular and get the desired profit from the sales. And one of the first steps of E-shop promotion is the composition of semantic kernel. To learn how to compose semantic kernel for E-shop will be described further.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Cd0407KWwAA5Np7.jpg\"><img class=\" size-full wp-image-2596 aligncenter\" src=\"http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Cd0407KWwAA5Np7.jpg\" alt=\"Cd0407KWwAA5Np7\" width=\"600\" height=\"401\" /></a>\r\n\r\nThe semantic kernel of any website can be introduced like well-ordered set of search words and phrases that most accurately characterize goods and services offered on the website. E-shop semantic kernel includes the key-words connected with the buying of goods which are represented on the site. Definite information requests can stand for semantic kernel as additional criteria.\r\n\r\nTo compose semantic kernel for E-shop you should bring all basic queries together. Basic queries are the requests which in general characterize goods of E-shop. For example, if the E-shop is specialized in selling of mobile phones and computer technologies then it needs “mobile phone”, “iPads”, “computers”, “electronic books” to be basic.\r\n\r\nWhen the basic requests are chosen it is necessary to enlarge given positions by making it more concrete and specific. To make queries more exact is better to add important characteristics of goods, mentioning of cities and regions which are connected with the E-shop. Also words such as “buy”, “order” are preferable too. If we take as an example the E-shop of mobile phones and computer technologies, the list of requests would include words such as \"mobile phone + brand’s name\", \"tablet + diagonal size\", \"computers + buy + city or region \"and others.\r\n\r\nWhile working-out of queries’ lists it’s necessary to check each of 