ne domination. Find out how our SEO San Diego Company can take you to the top of Google.','Website Support and Online Consultant Efficiency Increase','','publish','closed','closed','','website-support-online-consultant-efficiency-increase','','','2025-10-20 10:09:22','2025-10-20 07:09:22','',0,'http://www.wiseswans.com/2016/12/31/website-support-online-consultant-efficiency-increase/',0,'post','',0),(1834,3,'2016-12-31 06:27:14','2016-12-31 06:27:14','&nbsp;\r\n<h2>E-Shop Usability: Main Features of Common Pages</h2>\r\nE-shop customers’ conversion depends on many factors, where usability is definitely one of the major. Usability must be the key matter for designers from the very beginning of the e-shop project. Whatever, if e-shop already operates, its usability must be carefully checked.\r\n\r\nE-shop usability analysis demands detailed evaluation of nearly every page, as there must be no any undervalued factors for customers’ conversion. Firstly, the attention must be paid to common pages – catalogue, item description and cart.\r\n\r\n<em>Catalogue’s Usability</em>\r\n\r\nCatalogue is the heart of any e-shop as its design and convenience determine potential customers\' ability to find necessary items and make an order. No matter what e-shop offers, there are some main features:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>all items are correctly described and have a preview photo;</li>\r\n 	<li>filters and sorting work properly;</li>\r\n 	<li>each item on stock is available to put in the cart;</li>\r\n 	<li>unavailable items are marked accordingly;</li>\r\n 	<li>items on promo sales or ones discounted have special marks to be distinguished;</li>\r\n 	<li>adding item to the card is confirmed and visualized.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<em>Item’s Page Usability</em>\r\n\r\nRequirements to the item’s page are probably the strictest than any other. It should have an attractive interface, be available to promotion and easy to use. Here are some common parameters:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>page header contains the item’s name;</li>\r\n 	<li>page indicates correct and sufficient information;</li>\r\n 	<li>item’s photo is correctly shown on the page;</li>\r\n 	<li>there is a special button («Buy», «Add to Cart» or so on) that allows to place the selected item to the cart by clicking;</li>\r\n 	<li>if item has any options, all selectors and checkboxes work correctly;</li>\r\n 	<li>adding item to the card is confirmed and visualized;</li>\r\n 	<li>adding unavailable item to the cart is not allowed;</li>\r\n 	<li>all special promotions and discounts are clearly shown on the page;</li>\r\n 	<li>easy return from the item’s page to the main catalogue;</li>\r\n 	<li>up-selling and cross-selling tools work properly.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<em>Shopping Cart Page\'s Usability</em>\r\n\r\nShopping cart page is last but not least link in the purchase chain. Yes, potential customer can even refuse to buy item if he feels uncomfortable on this stage. To raise the usability of the shopping cart’s page, the following notes should be checked:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>all graphic forms must work properly;</li>\r\n 	<li>all items added to the cart are indicated correctly;</li>\r\n 	<li>item’s quantity is selected on the item’s page and/or can be manually changed in the specified field (by entering the number or by using «add»/«remove» buttons);</li>\r\n 	<li>total sum of the order is correctly calculated and all discounts, coupons, commissions are included;</li>\r\n 	<li>total sum immediately changes on every item adding/removing without need for the page refreshing;</li>\r\n 	<li>cart’s page has:</li>\r\n 	<li>link to the main catalogue;</li>\r\n 	<li>link to the order confirmation;</li>\r\n 	<li>add/remove buttons or similar links for items;</li>\r\n 	<li>there is no need to refresh the page after removing item from the cart.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAgain, all points listed above are very common and related only to main pages. Typical e-shop must also include info pages, order confirmation and checkout pages, search forms and others. Similarly, their usability must be carefully checked as well. To adjust or revise the usability and perform an optimization for the further growth it is advised to involve the professional web-studio to get personal solution.\r\n<h3 data-fontsize=\"16\" data-lineheight=\"24\"><strong>We are traffic generation experts </strong></h3>\r\nWiseSwans SEO Services has a proven track record of search engine domination. Find out how our SEO San Diego Company can take you to the top of Google.','E-Shop Usability: Main Features of Common Pages','','publish','closed','closed','','e-shop-usability-main-features-common-pages','','','2025-10-20 10:09:48','2025-10-20 07:09:48','',0,'http://www.wiseswans.com/2016/12/31/e-shop-usability-main-features-common-pages/',0,'post','',0),(1836,3,'2016-12-31 06:27:14','2016-12-31 06:27:14','<h2>The convenience of using B2B sites: what is important to take into consideration?</h2>\r\nSites those format are known as B2B (\"business to business\"), usually provide a different scenario of partnership with visitors, in contrast to \"business to customer\" type sites. For the creation of this sites it is important to think about the specifics of the convenience of using.\r\n\r\nCompanies that operating in the segment of \"business to business\" oriented not only on a one-time sale of goods or provision of services, but on a long-term cooperation. Now, we’d like to list some of the common basic features of the convenience of using sites.\r\n\r\n<em>Support after making a deal</em>\r\n\r\nSince the cooperation with a future client B2B site involves long-term cooperation, is very important to the visitors to know such information as with whom and how they will be able contact for support after the purchase of goods or performance of services. So information about further support should be presented in the B2B site.\r\n\r\n<em>Clients reviews</em>\r\n\r\nIn general, reviews of people that have already used the services of the company are always important, but for B2B sites, they have a special importance. For those who will be on behalf of the client to make a purchase decision, you need to make sure that the company can fully trust, because it is usually a significant amount. They help to dispel doubts about the real customer reviews already cooperating with the company.\r\n\r\n<em>Examples of using</em>\r\n\r\nThe so-called case studies or methods of using - one of the key elements of the convenience of using of this site. Future partners would like to know how another client have used the products in question. It is momentous here that the submitted case studies in such site were identified as precise as available and easily perceptible information.\r\n\r\n<em>Information about prices</em>\r\n\r\nOn the one side, business customers would like to have an understanding just what is the price of a particular commodity or group of commodities, and on the other - is not always possible to pre-calculate the exact price if the product is further adapted to the needs of each individual customer. As a result, if the prices of goods are formed individually for each business client, it is better not to introduce visitors to the misconception, pointing immediately to the pages of the price of goods. Conversely, if the price of each product is constant, there is no need to hide it.\r\n\r\n<em>Information about discounts</em>\r\n\r\nBear in mind, that on B2B sites purchases of the goods is usually comes to directly entire parties, discounts would be very interesting to the future buyers. Therefore, from the convenience of using standpoint B2B site will be useful to display on the page of product, how many will be able to save, if you order more goods. It will underline benefits from cooperation.\r\n\r\n<em>Repeated purchases</em>\r\n\r\nIn terms of usability may be useful to offer business customers a simple procedure of repeat purchases. For instance, if a client constantly gets the identical group of products, you can advise him to do a second purchase of an automatic. This thing will save time for every sides.\r\n<h3 data-fontsize=\"16\" data-lineheight=\"24\"><strong>We are traffic generation experts </strong></h3>\r\nWiseSwans SEO Services has a proven track record of search engine domination. Find out how our SEO San Diego Company can take you to the top of Google.','The convenience of using B2B sites: what is important to take into consideration?','','publish','closed','closed','','convenience-using-b2b-sites-important-take-consideration','','','2025-10-20 10:08:58','2025-10-20 07:08:58','',0,'http://www.wiseswans.com/2016/12/31/convenience-using-b2b-sites-important-take-consideration/',0,'post','',0),(1839,3,'2016-12-31 06:27:14','2016-12-31 06:27:14','<h2>How productive use favicon for your site?</h2>\r\nThe favicon of the site is the image with the following parameters: 16X16 or 32X32 pixels, which is visible along with the page title in the browser tabs or in the results of search systems. This element can actually have a big impact on traffic to the site, so the necessity of using it effectively is important to give value.\r\n\r\nCertainly it seems that a fairly small image is unlikely to have a major impact on potential visitors to the site, but the facts suggest otherwise: a notable and memorable favicon could become an additional incentive to click on the link to your website in the search results, and it is a plus to behavioral factors site and to the overall picture of attendance.\r\n\r\nIn order to favicon for the site was the most productive, the creation of this thing must be approached with the same care and responsibility, as well as the creation of other components in the design of the site. Now look at some important features of favicon.\r\n\r\n<em>The uniqueness of the favicon</em>\r\n\r\nIf a website is created with the help of ready-management systems (CMS), then it has a standard favicon such a system can be installed. Therefore, favicon 