s such as \"delivery\", \"order\", \"buy\". In most cases, the search at the request of the system, containing such words form a geographically sensitive issue, based the assumption that in this case, users are interested in the local sites, not sites in other regions.\r\n\r\nNote the request of the city name, province/region or country, in fact, no evidence of a geographical relationship: if the request is the name of a specific geographic region or locality, this request is a regional issue and the search for such thing is created differently.\r\n\r\nThere are several ways to check the geographic dependence of requests in the promotion of sites that help you learn as accurately geographically dependent on whether the interests of the search request or not. For example, you can enter a request into a search system, the search by specifying the settings first one region, and then - another. These SERPs then need to compare with each other. If in the first places of each of the renditions will be the sites of the selected regions, the introduction of a request really is geographically dependent.\r\n\r\nMembership of a particular search query to geographically dependent is an important cause that affects the selection of appropriate thematic queries for site promotion: for example, if a web resource is progressing in specific regions, the use of geographically dependent request will be favorable for him, but for the promotion of sites which should take a higher position in the overall search results, it is better to choose, on the contrary, geographically independent inquiries.\r\n<h3 data-fontsize=\"16\" data-lineheight=\"24\"><strong>We are traffic generation experts </strong></h3>\r\nWiseSwans SEO Services has a proven track record of search engine domination. Find out how our San Diego SEO can take you to the top of Google.','The concept is geographically dependent requests in the promotion of sites','','publish','closed','closed','','concept-geographically-depend