e card is 120 by 120 pixels. And the image file size must be less than one megabyte.\r\n\r\n<em>Summary Type with Large Image.</em> This card is the same as in the first variant, but a picture that is contained in it may be longer. Its location is above the title and description card. The minimum width of the image - 280 pixels and the minimum height - 150 pixels. And the image file size must be less than one megabyte.\r\n\r\n<em>Photo Type.</em> The card is located in the center of the image messages and it plays a major roll. Title in the card cannot be.\r\n\r\n<em>Gallery Type. </em>The card, which immediately has a few images (gallery). This type of card allows you to add to the message to four different images, as well as to put their author. Title and description are in this optional card.\r\n\r\n<em>App Type. </em>The card gives extensive information about the application. This card allows you to specify the name of the application, give it a description, and add an icon. Also it is possible to add data on the price and rating of the app. This type of card is supported only in iOS and Android clients, but is not available for the web.\r\n\r\n<em>App Installs and Deep-Linking.</em> This extension allows you to enhance the functionality of existing cards. With the help of this extension is possible, for example, add to tweet you can download the application. It only works for iPhone, iPad and Android (Google Play).\r\n\r\n<em>Player Type. </em>The card adds a media player (audio or video) to the tweet. Longer requires acknowledgment, unlike other types of cards.\r\n\r\n<em>Product Type.</em> This card is designed for enhanced performance in tweet information about the product. It may contain a title with the name of the product, information on the price and place of purchase, the product description and a photo of him.\r\n\r\nIn order to add a page for your card, you must choose among the above types need and then fill in the value for the page group Meta tag a