,2558,'http://rightonit1/?post_type=acf-field&p=2559',0,'acf-field','',0),(2560,3,'2025-10-19 13:42:31','2025-10-19 10:42:31','','Блок архива проектов для главной','','publish','closed','closed','','%d0%b1%d0%bb%d0%be%d0%ba-%d0%b0%d1%80%d1%85%d0%b8%d0%b2%d0%b0-%d0%bf%d1%80%d0%be%d0%b5%d0%ba%d1%82%d0%be%d0%b2-%d0%b4%d0%bb%d1%8f-%d0%b3%d0%bb%d0%b0%d0%b2%d0%bd%d0%be%d0%b9','','','2025-10-19 13:42:31','2025-10-19 10:42:31','',0,'http://rightonit1/?post_type=custom_block&#038;p=2560',0,'custom_block','',0),(2561,3,'2025-10-19 13:43:16','2025-10-19 10:43:16','','Home','','inherit','closed','closed','','12-revision-v1','','','2025-10-19 13:43:16','2025-10-19 10:43:16','',12,'http://rightonit1/?p=2561',0,'revision','',0),(2562,3,'2025-10-19 13:49:08','2025-10-19 10:49:08','','Home','','inherit','closed','closed','','12-revision-v1','','','2025-10-19 13:49:08','2025-10-19 10:49:08','',12,'http://rightonit1/?p=2562',0,'revision','',0),(2564,3,'2016-12-31 06:28:32','2016-12-31 06:28:32','&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You may have heard of a copywriter, or if you’ve been researching the web, a “SEO copywriter.”  At this point, you know the term and perhaps have a rough idea of what a copywriter does.  This article will help you understand what a copywriter specifically does.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Before you read too far, just know that a copywriter is one of the most valuable tools your business can have, and doubly so if you’re trying to expand your online business efforts.</span>\r\n\r\n<strong>Copywriter Vs. SEO Copywriter:  What’s the Difference?</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you’re used to working at a traditional company, you may have used a copywriter for your written business materials.  If you never knew the copywriter for your business, then you’re probably familiar with those letters you get in the mail attempting to sell you car or health insurance.</span>\r\n\r\n<strong>Those letters are the work of a traditional copywriter.</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">However, as you might already know, paper is quickly disappearing and everything’s becoming digital.  Nowadays, true traditional copywriters are becoming increasingly scarce, and instead SEO copywriters replace them.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The primary difference between the two is that SEO copywriters know how to write so the content they create gets found in the search engines, but at the same time, they can move people with words in order to get them to take purchasing action.  Basically, they’re similar to a traditional copywriter, but they have an additional skill to bring to the table in SEO.</span>\r\n\r\n<strong>Skills an SEO Copywriter Brings to Your Business That Make Him or Her Indispensable</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Now you know basically that SEO copywriters exist to bring more sales to your company through the written web content.  But, you may not know the specific steps and skills a copywriter possesses that make them critical to the success of your business.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><em>Here are some of those skills</em>:</span>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">  <strong>Effective Copywriting Techniques</strong></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What works with web copy is much, much different than what used to work with traditional print copy.  In the old days of marketing, formal language and a very businesslike/corporate image bought trust with consumers.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><em>Now, the game has totally changed</em>.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Any leading internet marketing expert knows that casual, personal language is what sells to consumers online these days.  They’re in a rush, so they don’t have time to read through dense jargon.  Plus, the web has made direct connections between consumers and agencies much more possible, so consumers expect you to speak as though you are having a casual conversation directly with them.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Because the web makes attention spans so short, professionals know how to quickly capture and maintain consumer attention.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It’s not easy, and it’s definitely a science of its own.</span>\r\n<ol start=\"2\">\r\n 	<li><strong>  SEO Knowledge</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ideally, you have an entire SEO/internet marketing company helping you with your internet marketing efforts, so not too much of this falls on the copywriter.  Your copywriter will at least know the basics – how to write for the web, where to place keywords, and how frequently to place them so that Google doesn’t get upset and dock the rankings of your content.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Some copywriters bring additional SEO skills to the table, such as keyword research.  Copywriters who know how to conduct keyword research can help you rank the pages they create much faster than a copywriter who does not.  To you, that means more traffic and sales in a shorter time frame.  Picking the wrong keywords can take years, if ever, before you rank your pages where people find them.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Other copywriters can give you more general SEO tips to help increase your web rankings.  Although a copywriter’s job is to write copy that brings in sales, if you find one that knows much about SEO as well, you’ve found a great bonus.</span>\r\n<ol start=\"3\">\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">  <strong>Designs Every Page with a Business Goal in Mind</strong></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Many internet marketing companies fall into the trap of creating more content and pages for Google.  The truth is those pages possess a very limited amount of value – they only please Google, not the people who visit them.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Every page a copywriter creates for your website must somehow keep the visitors there, or making a purchase. Each page must contain at least a primary keyword, and perhaps 1-2 variations of that keyword.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This gives the page the best chance to rank highly, attract traffic, and keep the visitor on-site somehow.</span>\r\n<ol start=\"4\">\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">  <strong>Develops Compelling Calls to Action</strong></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The written call-to-action either comes at the very end of the content, or 1-2 places throughout the content, depending on the type of content being written.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">From a business perspective, you know what your visitors should do when visiting your website.  But, they’re unlikely to take the action you want them to unless you ask and give them a very good reason to do so.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Offering a free e-book in exchange for contact information is one small way to stay in touch with visitors to your website.  Your company might also offer a free product when people order 3.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you’re not sure what to do, a skilled copywriter helps you to identify ideas for calls to action.</span>\r\n<ol start=\"5\">\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">  <strong>Writes Amazing Headlines</strong></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Headlines are more critical to your website’s success than ever before.  They have 2 important elements:</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The primary keyword must be included in them somewhere, and ideally near the beginningThey must be interesting, enticing, or communicate a benefit to the reader</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Why are headlines so critical?  Run any old search in Google.  Check out this one I did on “womens shoes:”</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Of these 3 results, which do you want to click on?  Man, FREE shipping from Zappos?  That’s what women want to click on.  See result #2?  That tells you what’s there, but the incentive is hidden below the headline, and crum, it’s only on orders over $35.  Nordstrom is somewhat on target – they have a sale going on, but what kind of sale?  How much is the discount?  Darn, and women have to read to figure out more about the free shipping.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If Zappos specificed what you had to do to get free shipping, it would have nailed the headline game.  I think they do free shipping on all orders, so that should be in the headline to make it absolutely killer.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It only takes a few seconds to read past the headline, but this is not something that internet searchers are willing to do, especially if one result makes it easy to learn everything in the headline!</span>\r\n<ol start=\"6\">\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">  <strong>A Lot of Research</strong></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Anyone can put together words that flow well.  But, only a few understand all the background research necessary to really make those sales happen.  A copywriter performs extensive research on the audience to know what it is that motivates them to buy.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In addition, he or she also gets to know the company very well so that the copy accurately reflects the company’s personality, making it distinct from other companies offering a similar product/service.</span>\r\n<ol start=\"7\">\r\n 	<li><strong>  General Marketing Knowledge</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You’re really getting excellent value if your copywriter acts basically as a marketing consultant.  A truly valuable SEO copywriter can give you ideas on how to differentiate from the competition, how to structure  your website for best SEO/web rankings, how to design landing pages visually to maximize conversions, and also how to design your whole website for the best user experience.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you encounter a SEO copywriter with this type of knowledge, hang on to them, even if you think they’re high priced – they are worth much, much more than what you pay them.</span>\r\n\r\n<strong>Copywriters Do More, But Those are the Basics</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The level of detail required to explain what a copywriter does and why would take many, many blog posts to cover.  But for now, at least you have a general idea and a reasonable answer to the question:  ”What does a copywriter do?”</span>\r\n\r\nWise Swans <a href=\"http://rightonit1/\">SEO Company</a> For You!','So, What Does a Copywriter Really Do?','','publish','closed','closed','','so-what-does-a-copywriter-really-do','','','2025-10-20 09:13:53','2025-10-20 06:13:53','',0,'http://www.wiseswans.com/2016/12/31/so-what-does-a-copywriter-really-do/',0,'post','',0),(2565,3,'2025-10-19 14:43:43','2025-10-19 11:43:43','&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gеttіng frее Intеrnеt mаrkеtіng tірѕ саn сut уоur lеаrnіng сurvе drаѕtісаllу whеn іt соmеѕ tо ѕtаrtіng аn оnlіnе buѕіnеѕѕ іn hореѕ оf mаkіng mоnеу оnlіnе nоw.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sеttіng uр аn Intеrnеt mаrkеtіng buѕіnеѕѕ саn bе а wіѕе dесіѕіоn іf уоu’rе ѕtаrtіng wіth lіttlе оr nо mоnеу аnd hаvе thе dеѕіrе tо ѕuссееd.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gеttіng Intеrnеt mаrkеtіng tірѕ аnd lеаrnіng frоm оthеrѕ trіаlѕ аnd еrrоrѕ саn ѕаvе уоu а lоt оf wаѕtеd tіmе аnd еffоrt іn trуіng dіffеrеnt орtіоnѕ аnd tесhnіquеѕ.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mаnу ѕuссеѕѕful nеtwоrk mаrkеtеrѕ tоdау wіll tеll уоu thаt thеу trіеd mаnу аvеnuеѕ lооkіng fоr ѕuссеѕѕ оn thе Intеrnеt аnd lеаrnіng tо ѕtаrt аn оnlіnе buѕіnеѕѕ іѕn’t аlwауѕ аn еаѕу tаѕk. Cоllесtіng ѕоmе іntеrnеt mаrkеtіng tірѕ саn mаkе ѕеttіng uр уоur buѕіnеѕѕ muсh еаѕіеr.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Intеrnеt mаrkеtіng tірѕ thаt уоu саn uѕе іѕ tо lеаrn ѕоmе bаѕіс соmрutеr ѕkіllѕ, оftеn јuѕt rеquіrіng сору аnd раѕtе knоwlеdgе. Yоu dоn’t hаvе tо bесоmе а рrоgrаmmеr tо bе ѕuссеѕѕful.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Lеt’ѕ tаkе а lооk аt ѕоmе оf thе <a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/Wise+Swans+LLC+SEO+%26+Web+Design/@32.7981932,-117.0137783,15z/data=!4m5!3m4!1s0x0:0x3bf7f3c72a59e658!8m2!3d32.7981932!4d-117.0137783\">Intеrnеt mаrkеtіng</a> tірѕ thаt уоu nееd tо gеt уоur оnlіnе buѕіnеѕѕ ѕtаrtеd.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">I wоuld еnсоurаgе уоu tо ѕіt dоwn аnd fіrѕt drаw uр а рlаn. Allоw уоurѕеlf tо drеаm аbоut whаt ѕuссеѕѕ wіll lооk lіkе оnсе уоu hаvе асhіеvеd іt. It’ѕ іmроrtаnt tо hаvе а wоrthwhіlе drеаm аnd tо knоw аnd undеrѕtаnd whаt іt іѕ bесаuѕе thаt wіll mаkе уоu реrѕіѕtеnt іn рurѕuіng іt tо thе еnd. All thе іntеrnеt mаrkеtіng tірѕ саn’t hеlр уоu unlеѕѕ уоu hаvе а wеll wrіttеn рlаn.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If уоu саn fіnd ѕоmеоnе whо’ѕ аlrеаdу ѕuссеѕѕful іn thе nісhе thаt уоu’rе рurѕіng, trу tо hіrе hіm оr hеr аѕ а mеntоr. Uѕіng thеіr еxреrіеnсе саn bе а hugе tіmе ѕаvеr аnd thеу саn ѕhоw уоu thе rореѕ wіthоut thе wаѕtеd tіmе thаt mоѕt Intеrnеt mаrkеtеrѕ fаll іntо. Gеttіng а gооd mеntоr саn ѕаvе уоu а lоt оf mіѕuѕеd tіmе, еffоrt аnd mоnеу.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Thеrе аrе а lоt оf wоrthlеѕѕ соurѕеѕ bеіng ѕоld tо nеw Intеrnеt mаrkеtеrѕ fоr tор dоllаr tоо, I mіght аdd ѕо dоn’t fаll рrеу tо іntеrnеt hуре. Sоmе gооd Intеrnеt mаrkеtіng tірѕ thаt wіll hеlр уоu gеt ѕtаrtеd іѕ tо thіnk аbоut thе thіngѕ thаt іntеrеѕt уоu. Dо уоu hаvе а hоbbу оr аn іntеrеѕt thаt уоu аrе раѕѕіоnаtе аbоut? Fіnd ѕоmеthіng thаt реаkѕ уоur іntеrеѕt, ѕоmеthіng thаt іѕ аlwауѕ оn уоur mіnd аnd ѕее hоw thаt mіght wоrk аѕ аn оnlіnе buѕіnеѕѕ.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Whеthеr уоu’rе іntеrеѕtеd іn ѕtаmрѕ, соіn соllесtіng, оr ѕurfіng, trу ѕtаrtіng а сlub аnd ѕеtuр а wеbѕіtе fоr thе mеmbеrѕ. Thіѕ соuld аttrасt nеw mеmbеrѕ frоm аrоund thе wоrld.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Blоggіng іѕ а grеаt tуре оf wеbѕіtе tо аlѕо ѕеtuр whеrе уоu саn ѕhаrе іdеаѕ, аdd а dіѕсuѕѕіоn grоuр аnd аllоw mеmbеrѕ аnd уоurѕеlf tо run аdѕ fоr whаt уоu hаvе tо оffеr. Bеѕіdеѕ thе рrоduсtѕ thаt уоur mеmbеrѕ оffеr, уоu mау аlѕо fіnd оthеr рrоduсtѕ оnlіnе thаt fіt іntо thе nісhе thаt уоu’vе сhоѕеn.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Thе rеаѕоn blоgѕ аrе ѕо grеаt аt gеttіng аttеntіоn fоr а nеw рrоduсt оr ѕеrvісе, іѕ thе fасt thаt уоu саn ѕtаrt tо оffеr уоur аdvісе аnd еxреrtіѕе аbоut а сеrtаіn hоbbу оr іntеrеѕt thаt уоu mіght hаvе. Onсе уоu ѕtаrt ѕhаrіng vаluаblе іnfоrmаtіоn, оthеrѕ ѕtаrt tо lооk аt уоu аѕ аn аuthоrіtу оn thе ѕubјесt, аnd реорlе lоvе tо рlау fоllоw thе Lеаdеr.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Onсе уоu hаvе ѕеtuр уоur wеbѕіtе уоu wаnt tо аutоmаtе іt аnd рrоmоtе іt tо реорlе thаt аrе оutѕіdе оf уоur сlub. Onе Intеrnеt mаrkеtіng tір thаt hаѕ wоrkеd wеll fоr mаnу іѕ tо ѕtаrt а nеwѕlеttеr fоr еvеrуоnе іntеrеѕtеd іn уоur nісhе. Yоu саn аutоmаtе thіѕ рrосеѕѕ bу аddіng аn аutо rеѕроndеr tо уоur ѕіtе. Sіmрlу рlасе а ѕіgnuр fоrm wіth а hеаdlіnе іntrоduсіng уоur nеwѕlеttеr аnd еnсоurаgе оthеrѕ tо орt іn, іf thеу wоuld lіkе mоrе іnfоrmаtіоn.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Onсе уоu ѕtаrt а nеwѕlеttеr аѕk уоu mеmbеrѕ tо соntrіbutе thеіr іdеаѕ аnd tірѕ ѕо thаt thеу саn bе ѕhаrеd wіth thе grоuр. Thіѕ gеtѕ еvеrуоnе іnvоlvеd. Uѕіng аn аutо rеѕроndеr аnd аutоmаtіng уоur mаіlіngѕ іѕ bу fаr оnе оf thе bеѕt Intеrnеt mаrkеtіng tірѕ thаt уоu соuld rесеіvе. Trуіng tо dо mаіlіngѕ аnd kеер uр wіth а mеmbеrѕ lіѕt wіthоut оnе іѕ nеаrlу іmроѕѕіblе.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Onсе уоu hаvе а fеw hundrеd mеmbеrѕ аnd уоu’rе ѕеndіng оut уоur nеwѕlеttеr wееklу оr bі mоnthlу уоu саn ѕtаrt tо аdd ѕоmе аdvеrtіѕіng аt thе bеgіnnіng оr thе еnd оf thе рublісаtіоn. Mоѕt реорlе dоn’t mіnd thіѕ іn аnуwау. Pеорlе tеnd tо еxресt thіѕ bесаuѕе thеу knоw thаt уоu dо hаvе ѕоmеthіng саllеd “оvеrhеаd.”</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If уоu сhоѕе tо ѕеtuр а blоggеr ѕіtе fоr dіѕсuѕѕіоnѕ аnd соmmеntѕ, уоu mау fіnd іt uѕеful tо ѕеtuр а mоrе соmmеrсіаl tуре wеbѕіtе аnd јuѕt оffеr а dіrесt lіnk frоm thе blоg оvеr tо thе оthеr ѕіtе. Runnіng аn Intеrnеt buѕіnеѕѕ іѕ аlѕо, “а dеаlіng wіth реорlе buѕіnеѕѕ” ѕо ѕеttіng uр а соmmеrсіаl ѕіtе mау bе lеѕѕ оffеnѕіvе tо ѕоmе mеmbеrѕ whо јuѕt wаnt tо uѕе thе сhаt rооm оr еntеr іntо dіѕсuѕѕіоnѕ wіthоut bеіng bоthеrеd bу аdѕ.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Othеr Intеrnеt mаrkеtіng tірѕ іnсludе еxреrіmеntіng wіth уоur ѕіtе, сhесkіng іt’ѕ lауоut аnd іt’ѕ еffесt оn vіѕіtоrѕ. Dо thеу ѕtау аnd lооk аrоund оr lоg оn аnd lеаvе іmmеdіаtеlу. I rесоmmеnd uѕіng Gооglе Anаlуtісѕ tо kеер trасk оf уоur ѕіtе ѕtаtіс’ѕ.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Autоmаtіng уоur ѕіtе, аѕ muсh аѕ роѕѕіblе, аlѕо frееѕ уоu аnd уоur tіmе uр tо lооk fоr mоrе іnfоrmаtіоn tо ѕhаrе оr fоr оthеr рrоduсtѕ thаt mіght bе а fіt fоr thе nісhе thаt уоu’vе сhоѕеn.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A rесіре fоr ѕuссеѕѕ іѕ tо аlwауѕ bе lооkіng fоr nеw соntеnt. Dоn’t lеt уоur ѕіtе gеt ѕtаlе оr реорlе wіll hаvе nо rеаѕоn tо соmе bасk іf thе mаіn раgе аlwауѕ ѕtауѕ аnd lооkѕ thе ѕаmе. Sоmеtіmеѕ fіndіng а bаlаnсе wіth blоggіng, gіvіng аwау frее аdvісе аnd оffеrіng соmmеrсіаl рrоduсtѕ іѕ а lіttlе lіkе wаlkіng а tіght rоре, іt rеquіrеѕ hаvіng gооd bаlаnсе.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">I hоре thеѕе Intеrnеt mаrkеtіng tірѕ hеlр уоu gеt уоur оnlіnе buѕіnеѕѕ ѕtаrtеd аnd уоu ѕtаrt mаkіng mоnеу оnlіnе nоw оr аѕ ѕооn аѕ роѕѕble.</span>\r\n\r\nWise Swans <a href=\"http://rightonit1/\">SEO San Diego</a>','Free Internet Marketing Tips For Starting An Online Business','','inherit','closed','closed','','1963-revision-v1','','','2025-10-19 14:43:43','2025-10-19 11:43:43','',1963,'http://rightonit1/?p=2565',0,'revision','',0),(2566,3,'2025-10-19 14:45:24','2025-10-19 11:45:24','&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<em><strong>Internet advertising business is really a term which includes all facets of marketing services or products online. </strong></em>\r\n\r\nNarrowing down a little, it means the company of strategic for that online promotion of the service or product. An Online marketing business includes smaller however equally essential activities  strategic web site design, compelling copywriting, SEO, search motor submission, reciprocal connecting, online campaigns, blogging, e-mail marketing, and a great deal else.\r\n\r\nOnline marketing business can also be known through other titles as internet marketing business, internet marketing business, and so on. Internet entrepreneurs are constantly trying to find and enhancing upon newer internet marketing strategies that will assist them drive increasingly more targeted traffic for their websites, leading to an improve in product sales. In additional words, an <a href=\"http://rightonit1/\">Online marketing</a> business is about exploring methods and choices that assistance and boost the broader advertising objectives of the business.\r\n\r\nAny newcomer towards the Internet advertising business should focus on seo, for probably the most traffic still involves websites through search engines like google and sites. Besides, she or he should learn how to generate targeted visitors online, carry out banner campaigns, write exceptional content, as well as improve general brand attention.\r\n\r\nA cement strategy is really a definite plus for just about any Internet advertising business. It gives you a measurable method to target your own market. This particular, in change, makes this easy for those who are searching for what you need to offer. They are able to find you easier and with no hassles.\r\n\r\nTraffic could be increased by search engine marketing techniques, or by utilizing ppc campaigns. Nevertheless, when everything is stated and carried out, it ought to be emphasized which traffic marketing isnít sales, and just about all visitors arenít customers. Therefore the next reasonable step would be to place your own attention about the visitors whoíve reached your website, and then try to convert all of them into customers of the service or product.\r\n\r\nAn Online marketing business differs in several vital ways from the conventional, brick-and-mortar company. One of these is the important thing factor associated with human conversation. When the visitor makes its way into a bodily store theyíre facing strong human interaction via a sales individual or clerk. During this particular face-to-face get in touch with, more compared to ninety percent from the communication that happens between both people is actually non-verbal within nature. An Online marketing business doesnít offer which scope associated with non-verbal conversation. Impersonal history code of the website storefront takes the area of comfortable human conversation. However, that problem could be solved through good content material positioning for those who have identified your target audience well sufficient.\r\n\r\nA<strong>n Online marketing business is simple to organize, nor could it be too costly.</strong>\r\n\r\nAll you need to do is strategy wisely as well as put which strategy in to action. Correct implementation is actually half the actual battle received.','Internet Marketing Business','','inherit','closed','closed','','1984-revision-v1','','','2025-10-19 14:45:24','2025-10-19 11:45:24','',1984,'http://rightonit1/?p=2566',0,'revision','',0),(2567,3,'2025-10-19 14:46:17','2025-10-19 11:46:17','&nbsp;\r\n\r\nEven the best intentions in designing and building a new website can run afoul when planning has not been well thought out. Add to the fact that making the wrong decision can cost you money. At the very least, you will wake up every morning, view your website, and wish that you had someone do it for you.\r\n\r\n<strong>WordPress Customization</strong>\r\n\r\nCustomization of Word Press can be a difficult process. The module for the website is written in the language of PHP. If you are unfamiliar with this common web programming language, then you might encounter difficulties in customizing your website.\r\n\r\nYou will have to upload a theme to your website in order for it to work properly. If you only use the layout that the theme provides, it can be enough for you to build a decent website, but if you plan on customizing it beyond the design of your theme, then you might have to consult with a web developer in order to get a customization that eliminates the generic look and feel of the website. Most themes consist of hundreds of files that run the website, and there never seems to be any standard as to where the original developer might have created certain coding actions that control how the website performs and responds to requests. A skilled web developer will be able to perform a certain degree of customization so that your website will look unique, with a personal touch that sets you apart from others.\r\n\r\n<strong>Hosting is Tied To Cost of Website</strong>\r\n\r\nSome web builder companies have a plan where you purchase the website and then they give you free hosting. One such company is called Weebly. If you choose the higher end of their web templates, then you will end up paying about 7 times more for hosting fees than you would if you signed up for a plan on any of the top 5 hosting services. Your choice of hosting should be an important consideration while you ponder building your website. If you should decide to leave your web builder company for any reason, you may not be able to transfer your website files to another hosting service. There are also companies that will not allow you to take your domain name when you leave them either. So prudent research into these web builder companies is vital if that is the route you are considering taking.\r\nAs discussed above, anytime you download a template that is built by someone else, you have limited customization. You are kind of stuck with whatever design is built into the template. Sometimes you are susceptible to copyright violations if you modify the template, so the agreement must be carefully read and understood before making any modifications.\r\n\r\n<strong>Targeting Audience</strong>\r\n\r\nWe are back on that subject, probably because it is so important. Does your template reflect the theme and message you want to show your audience? The wrong template can send the wrong message to your customers. The theme you choose could be someone else\'s theme that they picked, possibly with the same industry that you are in. That is why customization is so important, because your theme you bought for $40 is sold to many other people also.\r\n\r\n<strong>Exposure to Your Customers</strong>\r\n\r\nBasically a spin off that links into targeting your audience. But it needs to be incorporated into rankings which lead to customer exposure.\r\n<h2>You need to have good SEO (Search Engine Optimization) to gain exposure, which I will discuss later.</h2>\r\n<strong>Powerful and Professional Content</strong>\r\n\r\nCan you write powerful and professional content that is backed by compelling quality images? This is extremely important. A website that does not have the ability to capture visitors and entice them to further look into your website is not going to keep them on your website very long. Once they leave, they will likely not return.\r\n\r\n<strong>Does it look like a Professional Website?</strong>\r\n\r\nYour website is a direct extension of your company. If you have typos, broken links, poor quality images, poor layout, a weak call to action, or any other number of issues, then you and your company will be judged on the merits of your website. Visitors that are not impressed with your website are likely to look at your competitor\'s websites where they might have a better user experience, in addition to experiencing an easier time in finding what they are looking for.\r\n\r\n<strong>Wise Swans</strong> <a href=\"http://rightonit1/\">SEO Expert San Diego</a>','Seven Drawbacks for Do It Yourself Designers','','inherit','closed','closed','','1992-revision-v1','','','2025-10-19 14:46:17','2025-10-19 11:46:17','',1992,'http://rightonit1/?p=2567',0,'revision','',0),(2568,3,'2025-10-19 14:47:27','2025-10-19 11:47:27','&nbsp;\r\n<h2>SEO or Search Engine Optimization is a continual process that is never exhaustive.</h2>\r\nIt is vital to achieving and maintaining your rankings in the search engines, which in turn results in driving traffic to your website. Below are only a few of the many practices that enable preparation for ranking your website.\r\n<h3>Naming Conventions</h3>\r\nSEO begins with the initial building of your website. The names that you give your files have a huge impact on SEO. You need to have names that the google bots will associate with the content of your website. It is also important to determine in advance on how you want to join multiple words in your naming. Do you want to use a hyphen or an underscore? While this decision is irrelevant in your rankings, it is still a good idea to be consistent, to avoid a broken link on your files by not following your normal flow of file naming.\r\n<h3>Link Structure</h3>\r\nWhat you name your links can also have a great impact on <a href=\"http://rightonit1/seo-and-organic-search-ranking/\">SEO</a>. You should name your links in relation to what the content of these links contain. Do not be afraid to put more than a few words into your links. I believe Google will allow an almost unlimited number of characters but to play it safe, I would keep it down to about 60.\r\n<h3>Page Title</h3>\r\nThis is also very important. Your title should be carefully thought out because Google needs to determine what your page is all about. You can choose to put in as many words in your title as possible but keep in mind that if you use more than 5 or 6 words then Google might not display your page title properly.\r\n<h3>Meta Descriptions and Meta Keywords</h3>\r\nThese should also be carefully thought out. You will want to place these words so that they match some of the first 50 words in your text. And remember not to stuff your keywords because Google will think you are spamming if you do so. More importantly is an accurate Meta description. If you have the wrong or inaccurate Meta descriptions and keywords, it will hurt your rankings.\r\n<h3>Image Title</h3>\r\nAlthough it may not seem important, it is indeed important to Google. The bots do not read or recognize the actual images, and that is why it is so important to properly title your images, because that is the only clue that the bots have that describes your image. You should also give an accurate description in the Alt tag. There are some people that are handicapped and have to use alternative devices to view the internet; and will not be able to learn what your image is all about without the Alt tag. You can use up to 50 words, but do so with reason. Put in only the right amount of text that accurately describes the image.\r\nOne of the problems with Weebly is that when you name your image it does not translate to the Weebly system very well. If you give your image a name, Weebly will rename it and designate a numerical value, which can have a negative effect on your SEO.\r\n<h3>URL\'s</h3>\r\nURL\'s or Uniform Resource Locator is used by name servers to identify your website. Servers scan databases for your URL, while a domain name is searched on Name Servers. The servers are able to convert a URL into a domain name. It can sometimes correct an incorrect domain name, but if it cannot, then you will get a 404 error page returned to you.\r\n\r\nIf you are using Weebly, you write a blog article, and it does not differ between an actual domain name and a page structured URL. This could cause some confusion in the search engines because the Weebly system does not seem to care which one is used for blogs and which ones are used for permanent, structured web pages.\r\n<h3>Weebly and WordPress SEO</h3>\r\nIf your website resides on Weebly, you may want to use your analytics to insure you are getting the right volume of traffic to your website. Even though you do all the right techniques for SEO, some websites might still experience low traffic volume due to internal settings where your website resides. I cannot say whether this is intentional or unintentional, but it is well worth making the effort to regularly monitor your incoming traffic to see if there any issues that are affecting your website visibility and traffic flow. Word Press has a plug in that automatically sets up your SEO. You only have to install it and make a few adjustments to the settings.\r\n\r\nIf you plan on setting up a blog on Weebly, then you must accept the fact that if you choose to have your comments open to all, then you may get heavy spamming. Weebly does not allow you to moderate your comments such as in Word Press. This could have an effect on your SEO because you will get unrelated and unwanted links and spam, which can hurt a website.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://rightonit1/\">SEO Company</a> <strong>Wise Swans</strong>','Search Engine Optimization (SEO)','','inherit','closed','closed','','1991-revision-v1','','','2025-10-19 14:47:27','2025-10-19 11:47:27','',1991,'http://rightonit1/?p=2568',0,'revision','',0),(2569,3,'2025-10-19 14:53:09','2025-10-19 11:53:09','<h2>Internet Marketing – Use A Content Management System</h2>\r\nUse a quality CMS to build your content pages. It gives you control of your content which you will thank yourself for once you have many articles and sections. The search engines will favour the use of ‘legit’ software.\r\nA content management system seperates content from design, so even if you know nothing about website construction, you are easily able to add the crucial content needed for your website. You should focus your energy on your internet marketing strategy not your website development. A good CMS will solve this problem for you, however it is not an essential requirement, simply an option to make your life easier and allow you to focus on your internet marketing and promotion strategy.\r\nIts worth remembering that your software should be legitimate should you decide to use a CMS to run your website. In our experience this makes a considerable difference to some of the search engines. If you are running a shopping cart you should still have the ability to add pages of text content to your website. This is an important part of your internet marketing plan. So why are we advocating the use of a CMS?\r\nIn order to promote your site via search engines and their subsequent results your going to need content. A CMS allows you to log into your own site, add or modify content, then publish. When a new article is added the site menu’s are updated automatically thoughout your site. This in itself would otherwise be a time-consuming task if done manually. Your efforts can now be channelled toward your content input as part of your internet marketing plan, not spent fixing endless website problems or making code mistakes on pages.\r\n<strong><a href=\"http://rightonit1/services/\">Internet Marketing</a> – Keep It Clean</strong>\r\nEither way – keep it clean! Your code should validate and have no errors in the page. Use a CSS stylesheet to minimise the code on your pages and give you even more control of the look and feel of your site. In order to run a successful internet marketing campaign you must start from the ground up – if you have website problems fix them now before you get any deeper into your internet marketing plan.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://rightonit1/\">San Diego SEO</a> Company Wise Swans','Internet Marketing – Use A Content Management System','','inherit','closed','closed','','1980-revision-v1','','','2025-10-19 14:53:09','2025-10-19 11:53:09','',1980,'http://rightonit1/?p=2569',0,'revision','',0),(2570,3,'2025-10-19 22:01:34','2025-10-19 19:01:34','','E-Commerce Web Design for Hardwood Floors Website','','inherit','closed','closed','','72-autosave-v1','','','2025-10-19 22:01:34','2025-10-19 19:01:34','',72,'http://rightonit1/?p=2570',0,'revision','',0),(2571,3,'2025-10-19 22:17:09','2025-10-19 19:17:09','','aspire-desc-1024x682','','inherit','open','closed','','aspire-desc-1024x682','','','2025-10-19 22:17:09','2025-10-19 19:17:09','',72,'http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/aspire-desc-1024x682-1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(2572,3,'2025-10-19 22:17:19','2025-10-19 19:17:19','','aspire-desc-1024x682','','inherit','open','closed','','aspire-desc-1024x682-2','','','2025-10-19 22:17:19','2025-10-19 19:17:19','',72,'http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/aspire-desc-1024x682-2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(2573,3,'2025-10-19 22:17:24','2025-10-19 19:17:24','','aspire-mob-1024x682','','inherit','open','closed','','aspire-mob-1024x682','','','2025-10-19 22:17:24','2025-10-19 19:17:24','',72,'http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/aspire-mob-1024x682-1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(2574,3,'2025-10-19 22:25:28','2025-10-19 19:25:28','','Bowie Moving Company Web Design San Diego','','publish','closed','closed','','bowie-moving-company-web-design-san-diego','','','2025-10-19 22:30:09','2025-10-19 19:30:09','',0,'http://rightonit1/?post_type=project&#038;p=2574',0,'project','',0),(2575,3,'2025-10-19 22:23:55','2025-10-19 19:23:55','','bow-desc-1-1024x708','','inherit','open','closed','','bow-desc-1-1024x708','','','2025-10-19 22:23:55','2025-10-19 19:23:55','',2574,'http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/bow-desc-1-1024x708-1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(2576,3,'2025-10-19 22:23:56','2025-10-19