</a> ensures just that. Therefore, a company which furnishes its site with all the latest updates and information on relevant topics, that site would naturally be ranked higher in the search engine listings. This in turn, would encourage more visitors to the sites and naturally boost up the sales.\r\n\r\n<strong>Rules of adding new content</strong>\r\n\r\nWhen new content is being added to the website, it is very important to keep note of the fact that should be in context with the given topic and should not feel out of place. Next most important thing is to categorize the new content appropriately. One of the best practices is to keep upgrading the content of the site with client and customer feedback, product and service reviews and press releases. The more often content in a website is replaced with fresh and better quality content, the better are its chances of showing up amongst the first few results in the search engine listings.\r\n\r\n<strong>Importance of keywords</strong>\r\n\r\nNo matter what the content of each page of a website, it is always a better idea to furnish the on-page titles as well as the title of the webpage with high demand keywords or key phrase. Besides this, the short descriptions or summaries in the pages that depict the whole theme of the content must also be furnished with keywords and key phrases.','Fresh Content How Does it help in Search Engine Optimization?','','inherit','closed','closed','','1914-revision-v1','','','2025-10-20 09:23:06','2025-10-20 06:23:06','',1914,'http://rightonit1/?p=2686',0,'revision','',0),(2687,3,'2025-10-20 09:23:29','2025-10-20 06:23:29','','seo-charts-662x331','','inherit','open','closed','','seo-charts-662x331','','','2025-10-20 09:23:29','2025-10-20 06:23:29','',1911,'http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/seo-charts-662x331-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(2688,3,'2025-10-20 09:23:31','2025-10-20 06:23:31','&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWhen it comes to going global, the two significant elements to address all online businesses are chance of success and cost. The globalization of trade and technologies gives immense opportunities to every executive in making his or her business global. The internet is the place where you can introduce your services and products to the world and make your business global. <a href=\"http://rightonit1/\">SEO services</a> help your business to spread its wings in the virtual world and tap the potential customers of your products and customers.\r\n\r\nIn the starting stage of globalizing your business, you should know a website or portal where existing and potential customers can read and know about your services, products, business ethics and values. When you have an online business website and want more people to visit your site, it is only possible by the use of SEO services. Make use of affordable SEO services to ensure that your website is having maximum traffic. This is achievable only when your web portal is noticeable on the first or first few pages of search engine.\r\n\r\nSEO services carry out various activities so that your web portal gets visibility by search engines like Google, Yahoo!, etc when a user searches with specific keywords. SEO works on maximum Return on Investment (ROI) basis. SEO service uses various keywords that belongs to your article directory or blogs with which users are moved to your website from search engine.\r\n\r\nNumber of SEO service companies are available that will provide you with number of options. Professional SEO companies offer comprehensive SEO package that includes link building, content writing, <a href=\"http://rightonit1/selling-management/\">PPC management</a>, etc to globalize your business. They use different E-marketing methods and techniques to make your website visible. SEO companies ensure that the web pages are optimized to suit your website theme. The best SEO Company will help to increase the flow of traffic to your website and achieve top ranking in the search engines. Act attentively and smartly when hiring a new SEO company.\r\n\r\nSEO services can act as a medium to boost your online business. It is essential to understand that you require keeping up with other companies that have added a global facet to their business. Plan your business thoughtfully and impeccably execute it to ensure greater success for your business. With high rankings in search engines, SEO enables your business reap all the globalization benefits. It makes your business more visible and profitable.','Globalizing Your Business Using SEO Services','','inherit','closed','closed','','1911-revision-v1','','','2025-10-20 09:23:31','2025-10-20 06:23:31','',1911,'http://rightonit1/?p=2688',0,'revision','',0),(2689,3,'2025-10-20 09:24:12','2025-10-20 06:24:12','','google-animated-sign-1456230709-640x320','','inherit','open','closed','','google-animated-sign-1456230709-640x320','','','2025-10-20 09:24:12','2025-10-20 06:24:12','',1916,'http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/google-animated-sign-1456230709-640x320-1.gif',0,'attachment','image/gif',0),(2690,3,'2025-10-20 09:24:14','2025-10-20 06:24:14','&nbsp;\r\n\r\nProving the value of <a href=\"http://rightonit1/\">Search Engine Optimization</a> has become almost an obsession with most companies. So here are a few statistics that can help prove a point, either in favour or against an SEO investment. Also, experts now realise that convincing C-level executives to think of any SEO investment at all entails bandying about a few stats and figures because at the end of the day, it’s all a number game. So here they are:\r\n\r\nOf all the SEO campaigns, evidence has it that almost 40 percent of them have healthy returns of around 500 percent. In contrast, only 22 percent of Pay-Per-Click campaigns boast of success\r\nAlmost 62 percent users click on links available on the first page itself\r\nWhen a search is unsuccessful, 80 percent of users refine their keywords to search again\r\nNow if these stats don’t sway things in your favour then read on to discover the other things you can do to prove the value of SEO.\r\n\r\n<strong>Select the right time frame to measure SEO returns:</strong>\r\n\r\nIt’s smart to take seasonality into account. Depending on how frequently budgeting decisions are made think of a Year Over Year, monthly or quarterly time frame. Another approach to selecting the right framework is to think on the lines of Key Sales Periods. For instance, the hotel industry experiences spikes in enquiries at the weekends and during holidays and vacations. It’s easier to show the correlation between an increase in SEO activities and sales during such peak times. Then apply the following commonly used formula- Revenue- Investment/Investment multiplied by 100\r\n\r\n<strong>Be smart about customer profiling:</strong>\r\n\r\nAggregate data reveals nothing! Even organic keyword reports provide sketchy insights. What really works is segmentation or customer profiling for not all companies are interested in customer outside their region or country. Also not all companies benefit from customers who land on a blog and then move to the product page. Segments that are most useful in terms of calculating ROI include users who’ve filled up forms or made it to the checkout stage, geographic segments or visits to certain sections or your website.\r\nThere is enough to show that <a href=\"http://rightonit1/seo-and-organic-search-ranking/\">SEO</a> has value, and value that is immense. While it does not take very much to employ SEO to almost every business, it is only when the benefits start to show that you know just what you have gifted yourself. These measures alone can help prove the value of SEO to those who still remain skeptical about taking the plunge!','Proving the value of SEO','','inherit','closed','closed','','1916-revision-v1','','','2025-10-20 09:24:14','2025-10-20 06:24:14','',1916,'http://rightonit1/?p=2690',0,'revision','',0),(2691,3,'2025-10-20 09:24:57','2025-10-20 06:24:5