y links or deleting already paid links, it is very useful to know origin sites of incoming links. It will help to perform the analysis in general as well as in specific methods. That can be done by using various tools provided by search engines – Google Webmaster Tools, for instance.\r\n\r\nHow to check backlinks with Google Webmaster Tool?\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>On the Webmaster Tools homepage choose the site for analysis;</li>\r\n 	<li>Then enter the tool panel, select Search Traffic;</li>\r\n 	<li>In the popup menu click on Links to Your Site.</li>\r\n 	<li>After that, you will able to see the following data: number of domains that have links to the site and the number of links in each domain. Click on the specified domain to see details.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nDo not have an account in Webmaster Tool? Need to check backlinks on another sites (belonging to competitors, for example) to evaluate they? Probably, the most popular online service for site exploring and link checking is Ahrefs (ahrefs.com).\r\n\r\nThis service is chargeable. However, some functions are available for free (of course, with some limitations). Every visitor can check inbound links for one website once a day. To do it, type the desired URL in the field and then press Try It for Free. You will discover the number of backlinks, referred sites, links classes (dofollow/nofollow), links indexation (new and lost links) graph, the most popular link texts (also called anchors).\r\n\r\nThus, this service gives actual information and statistics regarding backlinks. According to Ahrefs’s restrictions for a free version, only five domains can be seen by unregistered users and maximum of ten are possible to see for registered users with free account. In a full (commercial) version of the service there are no such limitations.\r\n\r\nSo, it is very simple to check inbound links with these service tools. Nevertheless, it only the first stage. Then this data must be correctly evaluated to use it for optimization or for search engines promotion or to make complex competitors’ analysis. The recommended solution here is to involve the professional web-studio or web promo team into the process.\r\n<h3 data-fontsize=\"16\" data-lineheight=\"24\"><strong>We are traffic generation experts </strong></h3>\r\nWiseSwans SEO Services has a proven track record of search engine domination. Find out how our San Diego SEO can take you to the top of Google.\r\n<div id=\"spr_container\"></div>','How Backlinks Can Be Checked?','','inherit','closed','closed','','1870-revision-v1','','','2025-10-20 09:37:42','2025-10-20 06:37:42','',1870,'http://rightonit1/?p=2734',0,'revision','',0),(2735,3,'2025-10-20 09:38:07','2025-10-20 06:38:07','','affiliate-marketing-websitesuk-affiliate-websites-for-sale-how-does-affiliate-marketing-tyykgwvq-540x270','','inherit','open','closed','','affiliate-marketing-websitesuk-affiliate-websites-for-sale-how-does-affiliate-marketing-tyykgwvq-540x270','','','2025-10-20 09:38:07','2025-10-20 06:38:07','',1872,'http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/affiliate-marketing-websitesuk-affiliate-websites-for-sale-how-does-affiliate-marketing-tyykgwvq-540x270-1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(2736,3,'2025-10-20 09:38:08','2025-10-20 06:38:08','<h2><span style=\"background: white;\">What are affiliate web sites from the point of view of searching promotion?</span></h2>\r\nIn the case company has a number of sites, which are promoted at the same of similar topical searching requests, certain searching system sanctions can be imposed on one, or more, of them for so called affiliating. As a result, sites which are recognized by searching systems as affiliate go down in ranks and lose visitors. It will be said further about the ways of recognizing <em>affiliate web sites</em> by the searching systems and what do with these web sites.\r\n\r\nThe searching systems are operating effectively to reach the growing of effectiveness of their algorism, thus the new improvements appear. They help to clean the searching results from web undergrade sites, or web sites which don`t answer the users questions. <em>The cleaners for affiliation</em> is exactly one of such improvement, they deal with the availability of web sites of the same company.\r\n\r\nIf there are links leading to the several web sites of the same company in the adjacent places, it would lower the objectiveness of the searching results, that`s why searching engines try to avoid such situations. For this <em>a special group of cleaners</em> exists, which work is aimed on removal from the results ‘odd’ web sites of the same company. These are the cleaners for affiliate, and the web sites under their control are called affiliate in practice exploratory movement.\r\n\r\nFirst of all, the web sites with <em>identic or alike</em> domain info, IP address, possessor’s info, textual and media content, styling, structure, etc. are at the ‘risk group’ for getting the sanctions for affiliation. Of course, the more such matches the higher is a chance of facing the cleaners which mentioned. In addition, if the web sites are progressing at the same or related searches, the risk is increasing.\r\n\r\nYou can find a plenty of cleaners in searching systems, but how can we find out if the site was sanctioned definitely for affiliating? Some receptions can be used to do it. One of them is <em>to check all company web sites</em> which are moved by the same searching. If it shows that one web site is on the same positions but the others are extremely lowered in ranks, it is likely that these sites became the affiliate for the searching system.\r\n\r\nThe second technique for checking if the site was cleanered for affiliation is a usage of а <em>particular searching request</em>. For Google, is: “keyword&lt;&lt;(url=\"domain1.com\"|url=\"domain2.com\")”. Here the domain1.com and domain2.com are the addresses of the company`s web sites. If the check shows only one of the mentioned web sites, the other one is recognized as affiliate.\r\n\r\nIf the web site <em>fell under the influence of the cleaners</em> for affiliation as well as of any other cleaners, it will be rather difficult to go through this problem: you will have to ‘separate’ similar web sites and then to call maintainer of searching engines in order to exclude authorizations. So, of course, it is much easier to eschew affiliation taking right decisions in developing each of companies’ web sites.\r\n\r\nThe searching systems are opposed to them because they cause occupation of all popular results by one company, what is unacceptable. If different web sites of the company don`t try to occupy the searching results (<em>are promoted by different keywords</em>, work toward solving of various problems and have no matches) there will be no sanctions imposed on them.\r\n<h3 data-fontsize=\"16\" data-lineheight=\"24\"><strong>We are traffic generation experts </strong></h3>\r\nWiseSwans SEO Services has a proven track record of search engine domination. Find out how our San Diego SEO can take you to the top of Google.\r\n<div id=\"spr_container\"></div>','What are affiliate web sites from the point of view of searching promotion?','','inherit','closed','closed','','1872-revision-v1','','','2025-10-20 09:38:08','2025-10-20 06:38:08','',1872,'http://rightonit1/?p=2736',0,'revision','',0),(2737,3,'2025-10-20 09:38:33','2025-10-20 06:38:33','','24-effective-ways-to-get-free-marketing-03-650x325','','inherit','open','closed','','24-effective-ways-to-get-free-marketing-03-650x325','','','2025-10-20 09:38:33','2025-10-20 06:38:33','',1874,'http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/24-effective-ways-to-get-free-marketing-03-650x325-1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(2738,3,'2025-10-20 09:38:35','2025-10-20 06:38:35','<h2><span style=\"background: white;\">How to determine the most effective inquiries for your site promotion?</span></h2>\r\nMany website possessors would like to adopt all possible words and expressions inquiries from their sites’ semantical nucleus to develop their websites in the search systems successfully. The matter is that they mistakenly consider this way is the most useful. As the matter of fact, <em>to promote the website</em> with all its inquiries will be much more expensive and a little bit time-consuming. The best variant is to choose the most important inquiries and pay heed for them. There are several recommendations for you to determine the appropriate keys.\r\n\r\nActually, the site development always takes certain expenses. According to this, if you <em>promote more inquiries simultaneously</em>, you will go to more expenses. At one time, your expenses can appear extremely high so they can`t be recouped at all. As a result, any progress of your site will lose its sense. Anyway, you should try to avoid this situation. Thus it is necessary to find out what keywords are the most suitable right now to pay the greatest heed to.\r\n\r\nIn order to <em>select the most suitable inquiries</em> (words and expressions) for development of your site, you`d better to compare the forcefulness of each word with the expenses, spent on promotion. In the case when this process takes quite a long period of time but doesn’t attract enough guests on the site, your campaign should do without this key.\r\n\r\nThe <em>affectivity of searching inquiries</em> can be determined in various schemes, although more often we can judge about it by the number of inquiries and clicks. It means that an inquiry can be considered more effective when it is frequently used by users. The <em>expenses spent on promotion</em> are determined in their turn by the precise information about competitiveness in ranks, current positions in search systems and about a promotion cost prime.\r\n\r\nAs a rule, the process of the estimation of the affectivity of expenses, spent on determination of inquiries, is done manually or with a help of the automatic services. For instance, <em>frequency of inqui