margin and push the button “Send application”. Meanwhile sending this application can’t absolutely guarantee the entrance of your URL into indices or predict when your website URL will appear in the URL list.\r\n\r\nTo add information on a new web-resource into other search system’s database, let it be Bing, the website owner must use the same tactics. Every search engine system has the function “Report new website”, and website owners ought to use this tool if they want to add their website URL into database. To add the website address you must insert the URL of the new site into the margin and then push the “Add” button. Such applications are regarded solely as a recommendation to add your website into Bing’s search system, almost the same while adding into Google.\r\n\r\nAfter adding the website into indices, the search system may periodically visit your site to include into its database new data. Unfortunately it happens rarely, and much of the new information important for the target audience remains out of sight of search engines and this information can’t be included into search results. Acceleration of website indexing is a safe way-out.\r\n\r\nCrawler robots or programs which look for new information for adding it into search engine’s database, visit websites as often as new data is posted there. Besides, the Crawler’s visits depend on the quantity of the references. The more references – the more visits via those references.\r\n\r\nSo, to accelerate website indexing by search engines the website owner must either post often new information or get references from other websites which have high indexing rate by search engines (social networks, popular mass media, etc.). Those steps significantly increase the chances of new websites to appear in search results of different search engines.\r\n<h3 data-fontsize=\"16\" data-lineheight=\"24\"><strong>We are traffic generation experts </strong></h3>\r\nWiseSwans SEO Services has a proven track record of search engine domination. Find out how our San Diego SEO Company can take you to the top of Google.','How to accelerate website indexing by search engines?','','inherit','closed','closed','','1854-revision-v1','','','2025-10-20 10:02:33','2025-10-20 07:02:33','',1854,'http://rightonit1/?p=2762',0,'revision','',0),(2763,3,'2025-10-20 10:02:52','2025-10-20 07:02:52','','download-2-308x154','','inherit','open','closed','','download-2-308x154','','','2025-10-20 10:02:52','2025-10-20 07:02:52','',1852,'http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/download-2-308x154-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(2764,3,'2025-10-20 10:02:54','2025-10-20 07:02:54','Search engines are always improving and change their algorithms. So, for example, Google has ex changed its algorithm with a newer, named Google Panda 4.1. So they fight with bad web masters. Old methods for promoting of websites are getting less effective, but there are coming new, which improve the quality of the site. The biggest parts of the website promoting are natural links.\r\n\r\nWhat is the natural link? The Natural link is a link, which has written on the site, by users. So, for example, the user found a site, which seems useful and share it with his friends, by sending a link. The search engines count them as qualified links and don’t block them, because the act of sharing a link with friend’s proofs, that the site is good and interesting.\r\n\r\nThe list of differences of natural links, which are used for a website promoting:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Those links are on the donor page, when it is the first index by search robots</li>\r\n 	<li>They are easy to see by users of a donor site</li>\r\n 	<li>Those links are on the part of the page, where the content is, and not in a though block</li>\r\n 	<li>Natural links have the URL code of the page and they can’t be non-anchor</li>\r\n 	<li>There are many different, topical links on the donor site</li>\r\n 	<li>Natural links are on the sites, which have a high level of confidence