 general recommendations for improving the behavioral factors and they depend on the improvement of the quality of the site.\r\n\r\nThere are several types of these factors, namely, Clicks, which are interconnected with the search results, and internal - the factors on site. Clicks factors are: CTR extradition, the last and only clicks to issue and return to search results. And internal factors affect the number of visitors to the web page and the number of pages on the site, which has been viewed on the website is not returning from the search, bounce rate, average time on site, and so on.\r\n\r\nTo improve Clicks behavioral factors that can increase the positive representation of this site in the search results. To begin with, it must be done with a snippet - the short text, which is along with a link to your website in the search results. The thoroughly snippet matches the user\'s search, the greater the possibility that this page will open. And that this will increase the CTR website, which is one of Clicks behavioral factors.\r\n\r\nIf an Internet user enters the search of the link to the site and there will not find the required information, it will return to the search results. The more such returns, the lower the estimated relevance of site search, and the worse it is estimated appropriate behavioral factor.\r\n\r\nTo remedy this situation, you must meticulously take content pages on the site, so that they really correspond to the target users search queries.\r\n\r\nThe impact of the web resource owner Clicks behavioral factors is limited, so it is not possible to carry out the most complete control over the choice of users, even if the site is in the first position in search results, on average, only one-fifth of users take advantage of this link (according to the Google research). However, to implement the effects on behavioral factors can be internal to a greater extent so site owners usually take this factor into account firstly.\r\n\r\nTo improve internal behavioral factors must be engaged in the improvement of the site. This means that you need to work on the site, engaged in search of its greatest weaknesses. For example, if the site does not work usability, you must direct all our efforts to increase the level of this part, and if the site lacks the thematic content - have actively engaged in its content. At the same time, determine the appropriate methods of operation, you will need to take into account the peculiarities of the subject site: for example, there is no need to artificially delay the users on the site taxi service, because it is in this case it would be better if visitors are immediately able to fill an online application form or call on these numbers and call a taxi.\r\n<h3 data-fontsize=\"16\" data-lineheight=\"24\"><strong>We are traffic generation experts </strong></h3>\r\nWiseSwans SEO Services has a proven track record of search engine domination. Find out how our SEO Company San Diego can take you to the top of Google.','Some ways of improving the behavioral factors of ranking sites','','inherit','closed','closed','','1848-revision-v1','','','2025-10-20 10:04:10','2025-10-20 07:04:10','',1848,'http://rightonit1/?p=2770',0,'revision','',0),(2771,3,'2025-10-20 10:04:29','2025-10-20 07:04:29','','4.Brand-Promotion-Through-Instagram-540x270','','inherit','open','closed','','4-brand-promotion-through-instagram-540x270','','','2025-10-20 10:04:29','2025-10-20 07:04:29','',1844,'http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/4.Brand-Promotion-Through-Instagram-540x270-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(2772,3,'2025-10-20 10:04:31','2025-10-20 07:04:31','<h2>Promotion on Instagram and ways of increasing its efficiency</h2>\r\nNowadays Instagram is already recognized as a social network where users have their own accounts and use it for brand promotion. However, promotion on Instagram slightly differs from promoting via different social network like Facebook or Twitter and their ways of promoting 