rdering can be different ways. For example, in online stores to reduce the effect of product offerings in time or mark that number of units of a product is limited.\r\n\r\nIf the relevance, clarity and urgency proposals on the site to increase conversion rates, however, such a sign as a <em>distraction</em>, on the contrary, reduces the conversion, if a potential customer something online makes it impossible to complete the order form or add items to the cart, it is likely just out of this web page, and find the same offer from the company competitors.\r\n\r\nAnother factor that reduces the conversion - <em>anxiety</em>. The potential customer doubts in the decision to make a purchase or order, if the site has something that causes anxiety and lack of confidence, it could finally push the visitor. In the case of online shopping, disturbance can be tolerated unavailable contact information, the lack of clear information on the terms of payment and delivery, the lack of guarantees.\r\n\r\nShould be developed to increase the level of conversion of the design and content of the site so that the effect of all positive key factors intensified, and the negative - decreased. And in this matter without the help of a professional web studio simply cannot do: possession of a complex technique of creating and promoting websites, experts such studios will be able to offer the best solution for each case.\r\n<h3 data-fontsize=\"16\" data-lineheight=\"24\"><strong>We are traffic generation experts </strong></h3>\r\nWiseSwans SEO Services has a proven track record of search engine domination. Find out how our SEO San Diego Company can take you to the top of Google.','Conversion of the site and its factors','','inherit','closed','closed','','1840-revision-v1','','','2025-10-20 10:05:59','2025-10-20 07:05:59','',1840,'http://rightonit1/?p=2778',0,'revision','',0),(2779,3,'2025-10-20 10:08:58','2025-10-20 07:08:58','<h2>The convenience of using B2B sites: what is important to take into consideration?</h2>\r\nSites those format are known as B2B (\"business to business\"), usually provide a different scenario of partnership with visitors, in contrast to \"business to customer\" type sites. For the creation of this sites it is important to think about the specifics of the convenience of using.\r\n\r\nCompanies that operating in the segment of \"business to business\" oriented not only on a one-time sale of goods or provision of services, but on a long-term cooperation. Now, we’d like to list some of the common basic features of the convenience of using sites.\r\n\r\n<em>Support after making a deal</em>\r\n\r\nSince the cooperation with a future client B2B site involves long-term cooperation, is very important to the visitors to know such information as with whom and how they will be able contact for support after the purchase of goods or performance of services. So information about further support should be presented in the B2B site.\r\n\r\n<em>Clients reviews</em>\r\n\r\nIn general, reviews of people that have already used the services of the company are always important, but for B2B sites, they have a special importance. For those who will be on behalf of the client to make a purchase decision, you need to make sure that the company can fully trust, because it is usually a significant amount. They help to dispel doubts about the real customer reviews already cooperating with the company.\r\n\r\n<em>Examples of using</em>\r\n\r\nThe so-called case studies or methods of using - one of the key elements of the convenience of using of this site. Future partners would like to know how another client have used the products in question. It is momentous here that the submitted case studies in such site were identified as precise as available and easily perceptible information.\r\n\r\n<em>Information about prices</em>\r\n\r\nOn the one side, business customers would like to have an understanding just what is the price of a particular commodity or group of commodities, and on the other - is not always possible to pre-calculate the exact price if the product is further adapted to the needs of each individual customer. As a result, if the prices of goods are formed individually for each business client, it is better not to introduce visitors to the misconception, pointing immediately to the pages of the price of goods. Conversely, if the price of each product is constant, there is no need to hide it.\r\n\r\n<em>Information about discounts</em>\r\n\r\nBear in mind, that on B2B sites purchases of the goods is usually comes to directly entire parties, discounts would be very interesting to the future buyers. Therefore, from the convenience of using standpoint B2B site will be useful to display on the page of product, how many will be able to save, if you order more goods. It will underline benefits from cooperation.\r\n\r\n<em>Repeated purchases</em>\r\n\r\nIn terms of usability may be useful to offer business customers a simple procedure of repeat purchases. For instance, if a client constantly gets the identical group of products, you can advise him to do a second purchase of an automatic. This thing will save time for every sides.\r\n<h3 data-fontsize=\"16\" data-lineheight=\"24\"><strong>We are traffic generation experts </strong></h3>\r\nWiseSwans SEO Services has a proven track record of search engine domination. Find out how our SEO San Diego Company can take you to the top of Google.','The convenience of using B2B sites: what is important to take into consideration?','','inherit','closed','closed','','1836-revision-v1','','','2025-10-20 10:08:58','2025-10-20 07:08:58','',1836,'http://rightonit1/?p=2779',0,'revision','',0),(2780,3,'2025-10-20 10:09:21','2025-10-20 07:09:21','','10-Essential-Web-Based-Resources-for-Consultants-To-Improve-Their-Efficiency-260x130','','inherit','open','closed','','10-essential-web-based-resources-for-consultants-to-improve-their-efficiency-260x130','','','2025-10-20 10:09:21','2025-10