 that is associated with this card, then Twitter robot takes the information from the website of the cards and presents them in a so-called summary of the tweet.\r\n\r\nFormation of Twitter Cards done by adding html-code Web site Meta tags resources - their options are selected depending on the type of card. In total there are 8 kinds of these Cards.\r\n\r\nUsability Improvement.\r\n\r\n<em>Summary Type.</em> This card is the \"default\". It has a title and a description of the page on which the link leads, the picture is placed on a web page and some more information about the author. Minimum parameter for the image of the card is 120 by 120 pixels. And the image file size must be less than one megabyte.\r\n\r\n<em>Summary Type with Large Image.</em> This card is the same as in the first variant, but a picture that is contained in it may be longer. Its location is above the title and description card. The minimum width of the image - 280 pixels and the minimum height - 150 pixels. And the image file size must be less than one megabyte.\r\n\r\n<em>Photo Type.</em> The card is located in the center of the image messages and it plays a major roll. Title in the card cannot be.\r\n\r\n<em>Gallery Type. </em>The card, which immediately has a few images (gallery). This type of card allows you to add to the message to four different images, as well as to put their author. Title and description are in this optional card.\r\n\r\n<em>App Type. </em>The card gives extensive information about the application. This card allows you to specify the name of the application, give it a description, and add an icon. Also it is possible to add data on the price and rating of the app. This type of card is supported only in iOS and Android clients, but is not available for the web.\r\n\r\n<em>App Installs and Deep-Linking.</em> This extension allows you to enhance the functionality of existing cards. With the help of this extension is possible, for example, add to tweet you can download the application. It only works for iPhone, iPad and Android (Google Play).\r\n\r\n<em>Player Type. </em>The card adds a media player (audio or video) to the tweet. Longer requires acknowledgment, unlike other types of cards.\r\n\r\n<em>Product Type.</em> This card is designed for enhanced performance in tweet information about the product. It may contain a title with the name of the product, information on the price and place of purchase, the product description and a photo of him.\r\n\r\nIn order to add a page for your card, you must choose among the above types need and then fill in the value for the page group Meta tag associated with the selected card.\r\n<h3 data-fontsize=\"16\" data-lineheight=\"24\"><strong>We are traffic generation experts </strong></h3>\r\nWiseSwans SEO Services has a proven track record of search engine domination. Find out how our San Diego SEO can take you to the top of Google.','Website promotion and Online service Cards','','inherit','closed','closed','','1864-revision-v1','','','2025-10-20 10:12:18','2025-10-20 07:12:18','',1864,'http://rightonit1/?p=2789',0,'revision','',0),(2790,3,'2025-10-20 10:12:49','2025-10-20 07:12:49','','How-Book-Marketing-Uses-Social-Media-424x212','','inherit','open','closed','','how-book-marketing-uses-social-media-424x212','','','2025-10-20 10:12:49','2025-10-20 07:12:49','',1858,'http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/How-Book-Marketing-Uses-Social-Media-424x212-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(2791,3,'2025-10-20 10:12:51','2025-10-20 07:12:51','<h2>The concept of content marketing in the promotion of sites</h2>\r\nNowadays there are more and more new services, from which increases the popularity of sites and it helps to attract target visitors. One of such service is the content-marketing. This is a set of activities that help in the creation and dissemination of useful for the target audience of the site information in order to draw attention to this site. Let\'s talk about this concept as a content marketing and how it works.\r\n\r\nThe service in the field of promotion of sites is considered a relatively new but the essence of attracting targeted visitors to your website by placing useful and relevant information has been around for a very long time. Just before such a way to promote the site was optional, now it is used as one of the main.\r\n\r\nChanges in the algorithms of search system today have led to the fact that many of the methods and SEO techniques had been actively used in the promotion of sites, now it is not as effective. For example, if before the most famous sites in the promotion was a way of link building web resource; it is now only at the expense of a considerable number of backlinks a site cannot move. Therefore, requires new methods and procedures in the promotion of sites. Tech Support.\r\n\r\nAlong with the usual alternative method reference promotion just became content marketing. His basic idea is that you can earn the trust of the target users, using a variety of entertaining and publication of useful information for potential customers and assure target visitors of web page that it is the company\'s products or services promoted must be used.\r\n\r\nContent marketing, in contrast to the same promotion with the help of articles or press releases, is not focused on the dissemination exactly of advertising and this is its key feature. Content marketing is not directly advertise the specific product or service and introduces the potential target audience with the advantages of cooperation with the organization, provides information about various product innovations, generates impeccable image and increases the company\'s popularity.\r\n\r\nText - this is the main way of working content marketing to attract potential visitors. There are both topical articles on the site, as well as articles on various other resources, which include blogs, social networks, and forums. Also, together with the text information in the content marketing use videos, audio clips (podcasts), webinars, photos, info graphics. Than varied content with the promotion of sites, then more chances are greatly needed to seize the target audience.\r\n\r\nContent marketing is often contrasted with the traditional promotion in search systems that are just really, these two methods are important for the effective promotion together. Therefore, in order to increase the popularity of a Web resource and bring target visitors is better to choose not to search system optimization and content marketing alone and give preference to the integrated promotion to include the best method for each of these methods.\r\n<h3 data-fontsize=\"16\" data-lineheight=\"24\"><strong>We are traffic generation experts </strong></h3>\r\nWiseSwans SEO Services has a proven track record of search engine domination. Find out how our  SEO Company San Diego can take you to the top of Google.','The concept of content marketing in the promotion of sites','','inherit','closed','closed','','1858-revision-v1','','','2025-10-20 10:12:51','2025-10-20 07:12:51','',1858,'http://rightonit1/?p=2791',0,'revision','',0),(2792,3,'2025-10-20 10:13:08','2025-10-20 07:13:08','','download-3-252x126','','inherit','open','closed','','download-3-252x126','','','2025-10-20 10:13:08','2025-10-20 07:13:08','',1860,'http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/download-3-252x126-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(2793,3,'2025-10-20 10:13:09','2025-10-20 07:13:09','<h2>The concept is geographically dependent requests in the promotion of sites</h2>\r\nImportant role in the promotion of sites in search systems, for example, such as Google, is given the choice of geographically dependent requests. What is a geographically dependent request in the promotion of Internet resources? How does working with them can affect the outcome of promotion of the site in a given region? This will be our continued story.\r\n\r\nFor geographically dependent requests search systems create a special 