et audience, according to <strong><a href=\"http://rightonit1/seo-and-organic-search-ranking/\">online marketing data in San Diego</a></strong>.\r\n\r\nHow to make an illustration of a publication on social networks during the site promotion for the business correct today? The following main recommendations will help to identify it.\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>To pay attention to image formatting</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nIt is necessary to work with publication’s illustrating in social networks the same equal and responsible as with illustrating of texts on the site. This means that attention should be paid to formatting of the images: they must have high quality and meet the requirements of each social network size.\r\n\r\nIt is important to note that in case of exceeding the permissible image resolution, the special algorithms will automatically perform compression of these images to illustrate publications. As a result, the image quality can dramatically decrease. So it is useful to prepare images for posting on social networks, in this case the compression would be minimal.\r\n<ol start=\"2\">\r\n 	<li>To take images in accordance with the subject of publications</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nFor the illustration of publications on social networks it is very important to select the images that would fit the theme of a particular publication. For example, in some cases it is well to use photos ‘’before and after’’, in others - a photo of the goods used in the real world, in the third - a fascinating infographics, etc.\r\n\r\nSelecting the image source has a special significance in this case. So, it is the best to use the author\'s own image to illustrate articles in social networks, because less than \"jaded\" image will be - the better.\r\n<ol start=\"3\">\r\n 	<li>To find the ‘’flavor’’ in images</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nThe abundance of content produced by users of social networks is almost unimaginable. As usual in the popular and highly competitive subject areas it is quite probable to find ‘’fresh’’ ideas for photographs and drawings. Images with a flavor will solve the problem. For example, one can select images with unusual angles, unusual locations or original colors - this approach will highlight the publication among other similar and affect the emotions of users.\r\n\r\nPhotos and pictures in social networks are in the high demand. It is illustrated by the statistics activity in many groups and public pages of companies involved in <strong>online marketing in San Diego</strong>. So with the correct approach, one can ‘’make the most’’ of such an effective tool in a wish to attract attention. At the same time one should not forget that the approach of a promotion of social networks must be comprehensive: in addition to the thematic material publications it is also important to deal with the new members’ involvement in the group / page, to answer questions from users, to maintain the company\'s reputation in social networks.','Website promotion on social networks: how to illustrate the publication','','inherit','closed','closed','','1789-revision-v1','','','2025-10-20 10:16:01','2025-10-20 07:16:01','',1789,'http://rightonit1/?p=2805',0,'revision','',0),(2806,3,'2025-10-20 10:16:18','2025-10-20 07:16:18','','comp1-600x450-600x300','','inherit','open','closed','','comp1-600x450-600x300','','','2025-10-20 10:16:18','2025-10-20 07:16:18','',1793,'http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/comp1-600x450-600x300-1.gif',0,'attachment','image/gif',0),(2807,3,'2025-10-20 10:16:21','2025-10-20 07:16:21','<h2>Analysis of the competitors’ websites: Which criteria to compare?</h2>\r\nIf you are developing a site it is good to make an analysis of the competitor’s sites. So, you get to know what you should/could change and make your site the best and most comfortable to use.\r\n\r\nHow to start the analysis? At first, you should browse in the Internet for a website that covers the same sector of service, as you intend to provide. Choose only those websites, which are very popular and compare your own with them.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/comp1-600x450.gif\"><img class=\" size-full wp-image-2581 aligncenter\" src=\"http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/comp1-600x450.gif\" alt=\"comp1-600x450\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" /></a>\r\n\r\nSo, after you found a few competitors’ sites you have to decide how detailed the comparison should be. You can take either some criteria for a professional comparison or many. It is depending on the goals of the analysis. We will tell you of the most popular criteria below.\r\n\r\nThe attendance\r\n\r\nThe knowing of the attendance of the competitor’s site will help you to recognize how significant the competition between your and this site will be. If the competitor’s site has an open counter, you easy can get data from it. Otherwise, you can use a service of the web analysis, but in this case the information won’t be very exactly.\r\n\r\nThe age of the domain\r\n\r\nIf we compare an old site with a new one, then an old will have more privileges, because the browsers and users already have trust in this site. That’s why it is useful to know the age of the domain of your competitor’s site. Free online services WHOIS will help you to find this information.\r\n\r\nThe index in a search engine\r\n\r\nYou should make an analysis of the number of indexed pages of sites on the different search engines to give an assessment for the chances that your site will stand higher in a list of search pages than a competitor’s site. For make an analysis of checking indices in a Google search engine, you should type «site:https://address_of_the_site». In addition, you could use free online services for checking indices of sites.\r\n\r\nThe link profile\r\n\r\nThe quality of the incoming links in search engines takes large influence on the positions of sites in search engines. So, if it is possible, you should find out which incoming links your competitor does have. There are free services, which can give you not very exactly information about income links. On the other hand, there are services, which you have to pay, but there for you get exactly data.\r\n\r\nThe visibility in search engines\r\n\r\nThe part which shows your site in a search engine that notifies all available sites in the top list of the search engine is named “visibility in search engines”. You can get the most exactly data of the visibility in search engines if you use services, where you have to pay. But you also can do it yourself. For example, if the competitor’s site gets always high places in a search engine for different requests, you can be sure about the high visibility of your competitor’s site in search engines.\r\n\r\nSocial indicators\r\n\r\nToday, if you want to promote the website in search engines then you also have to promote it on social networks. So if the competitor’s site has a high visibility in social networks so he also has high visibility in search engines. If you want to make this analysis, you have to watch the visibility in social networks of a competitor’s site: If there are groups, numbers of people following them, numbers of likes and reposts. So if there are groups with more than one thousand followers, which give often likes and make reposts you can be sure it is a strong social indicator.\r\n\r\nOur <strong><a href=\"http://rightonit1/\">seo agency San Diego</a></strong> provides services, including analysis of competitor’s sites. We will give only exact data, so it will be easy to see what and how you should improve your own website. Our service includes developing and improving of the website. So you can contact us with every need about websites.\r\n\r\nSo make the right choice. <strong><a href=\"http://rightonit1/seo-and-organic-search-ranking/\">Seo San Diego ca</a></strong> will help you to make your dream come true.','Analysis of the competitors’ websites: Which criteria to compare?','','inherit','closed','closed','','1793-revision-v1','','','2025-10-20 10:16:21','2025-10-20 07:16:21','',1793,'http://rightonit1/?p=2807',0,'revision','',0),(2808,3,'2025-10-20 10:23:24','2025-10-20 07:23:24','','cm-qualitycontent4-804x402','','inherit','open','closed','','cm-qualitycontent4-804x402','','','2025-10-20 10:23:24','2025-10-20 07:23:24','',1821,'http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/cm-qualitycontent4-804x402-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(2809,3,'2025-10-20 10:23:26','2025-10-20 07:23:26','<h2>Quality Content in San Diego, CA</h2>\r\n‘Content is king’ is the phrase you will hear all successful SEO webmasters say. Writing content should never become a challenge, if it is then it probably isn’t relevant. Remember this content is the reason visitors are on your website, it needs to engage them, encourage them to share links to your website socially and on their own websites. Ask yourself these questions when writing content:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Are you copying information from elsewhere on the web?</li>\r\n 	<li>Are you offering real value to visitors?</li>\r\n 	<li>Are you padding out content to fill pages up?</li>\r\n 	<li>Are you encouraging visitors to seek more from you on other pages?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThese are some of the questions you need to ask yourself in working out whether you’re providing quality content.\r\n\r\nThe absolute worst content that exists today on the web is what the experts call ‘landfill content’, essentially this is when something is written purely to be bloated with several keywords and sometimes over use of a particular keyword. Occasionally you will come across articles and blog posts like this where you begin to notice there isn’t any actual content, just keyword babble.\r\n\r\nImagine for a moment you were in the magic bean business and looking to get your magic bean website found by search engines, the below example would be a terrible piece of content overly stuffed with keywords:\r\n\r\nWhen magic beans were first released to the general public they were a product with a high price tag as there were only a few firms who could offer magic beans. The price of magic beans has been falling ever since, and nowadays the magic beans market has filled with vendors trying to get a piece of the profit to be made from magic beans, the price is at an all time low.\r\n\r\nThe point of this content is to please or mislead search engines, and this could well achieve listings on the first pages of search results. If you imagine that every time the phrase ‘magic beans’ is used it links to the same website, that site would soon become pushed up the search results due to the sheer number of links to it using the same keywords.\r\n\r\nIf a visitor, or potential customer, experiences your brand in a low quality article like this it will give them a very poor first impression of your website or even your company. Impressing the search engines should never get in the way of impressing your visitors and ultimately as webmasters we should have pride in delivering high quality content that we are passionate about.\r\n<h3><strong>We are traffic generation experts </strong></h3>\r\nWiseSwans SEO Services has a proven track record of search engine domination. Find out how our SEO San Diego Company can take you to the top of Google.','Quality Content in San Diego, CA','','inherit','closed','closed','','1821-revision-v1','','','2025-10-20 10:23:26','2025-10-20 07:23:26','',1821,'http://rightonit1/?p=2809',0,'revision','',0),(2810,3,'2025-10-20 10:24:07','2025-10-20 07:24:07','','GoogleSEO-598x299 (1)','','inherit','open','closed','','googleseo-598x299-1','','','2025-10-20 10:24:07','2025-10-20 07:24:07','',1931,'http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/GoogleSEO-598x299-1-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(2811,3,'2025-10-20 10:24:25','2025-10-20 07:24:25','','url-optimization-tips-seo-friendly-url-structure-example-544x272','','inherit','open','closed','','url-optimization-tips-seo-friendly-url-structure-example-544x272','','','202