e useful for website promotion. A proper choice of platforms will help to market the website quicker and more effectively.\r\nThe texts of the links should be developed skillfully and should take into account the requests with which the websites are marketed. Also, it would be highly advisable that the links were in the body of the text which is in line with the topic of the marketed website. In such case website, promotion will go quicker and more effectively. Fulfilling the above actions has very positive influence on positions of the marketed website, and this fact confirms once more how important is the process of links development for website marketing.\r\nThe prepared links are placed on the platforms chosen in advance. Determining whether these platforms are suitable is also an important factor in the website marketing. The donor websites should be suitable for the search engines ranking point of view. The chosen platforms by no means should be under sanctions because it may put at risk the implementation of the project.\r\n\r\nFor this particular reason, Wise Swans entrusts the above works only to our high qualified employees.','Website marketing SEO for low frequency queries','','inherit','closed','closed','','1773-revision-v1','','','2025-10-20 10:45:42','2025-10-20 07:45:42','',1773,'http://rightonit1/?p=2877',0,'revision','',0),(2878,3,'2025-10-20 10:46:06','2025-10-20 07:46:06','','29-826x413','','inherit','open','closed','','29-826x413','','','2025-10-20 10:46:06','2025-10-20 07:46:06','',1775,'http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/29-826x413-1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(2879,3,'2025-10-20 10:46:09','2025-10-20 07:46:09','<h2>Proper semantic kernel for SEO</h2>\r\nBuilding the semantic kernel is a crucial work, which is, in essence, like constructing a foundation of all textual content of the website. The same as with foundation of the building, the mistakes made when building the semantic kernel lead to significant troubles in the futu