earch requests</strong></em>\r\nOne of the main rules of the optimizer to us the simplest requests. Frankly speaking, modern users are lazy, and do not go further than the first page of search results, and avoid complicated requests. For this reason the forward-thinking optimizer, remembering features of behavior of the Russian Internet surfer, selects the corresponding requests.\r\n<em><strong>Diversity of keywords</strong></em>\r\nSEO in several directions is a more complicated task, but the result of such work is more long lasting. Optimization for several requests simultaneously becomes an important way of modern marketing, especially, if the website volume is larger than a simple business card website.\r\n\r\nWith queries for <a href=\"http://rightonit1/\">SEO</a> everything is extremely clear.\r\n\r\nTo achieve a good result in website marketing you need to use the most used words that correspond to the topic of the website to the maximum extent possible, and at the same time to try covering the largest audience. It only remains to select these words.\r\n\r\nTo achieve a good result in <strong>SEO San Diego</strong> you need to use the most used words that correspond to the topic of the website to the maximum extent possible, and at the same time to try covering the largest audience. It only remains to select these words.\r\nFor these purposes there are special statics services that consider the queries entered by users, tying them to the date and the region from which the request came. It is very important for carrying out the events connected with geotargeting. Services of statistics allow selecting the most popular requests in various countries and even the cities, thereby optimizing the website for the desirable audience.\r\nThus you should not forget that in this world everything flows and, slowly, but changes. The popularity of search requests too. For example, the premier of the expected movie urges the interest to it in the Internet, and increase of average air temperature steadily leads to increase in number of requests concerning climate equipment. It is clear that these phenomena are temporary and the interest to such requests passes gradually.\r\nFor a long term website development more stable requests are used. Such requests will provide fixed number of target visitors without sharp splashes. But even among them gradual change of popularity is noted. Remembering it, the owner should eventually change the semantic kernel of the website in order to keep it relevant to the interests of the Internet users. Sooner or later technical support will be needed for updating content on the website of any complexity. Regularly performed works consist of upgrading its content (first of all text filling) according to statistics of various search engines.\r\nWe cannot say that this procedure is very frequent, but to keep the website in the TOPs and to develop the website this procedure should be carried out with known frequency. And upgrading content is a task which importance does not yield at all to initial forming of the semantic kernel discussed above. In this case work of the optimizer can be compared to strengthening of a readymade foundation or with its reconstruction, if there were found errors in the course of use.\r\nMarketing the website, in such way, looks like a constant process. Actually there is nothing strange in it, because the website just dies silently if no one takes care of it. At the same time growth and development of electronic commerce is not possible without constant technical support. The cost of this service is not so high as the income gained from the website, especially, if work was entrusted to the specialists capable of providing outstanding performance of the website.\r\n\r\nWise Swans SEO developes, creates, markets, and supports websites of any complexity level. A recipe of successful and the quickest marketing is a properly formed semantic kernel. This method is not new, but, currently it is the most effective development strategy of online resources. Ability to use all opportunities of <strong>search marketing</strong> is the distinctive feature which distinguishes true professionals - Wise Swans studio.','Proper semantic kernel for SEO','','inherit','closed','closed','','1775-revision-v1','','','2025-10-20 10:46:09','2025-10-20 07:46:09','',1775,'http://rightonit1/?p=2879',0,'revision','',0),(2880,3,'2025-10-20 10:46:24','2025-10-20 07:46:24','','elements-of-optimization-wheel-350x175','','inherit','open','closed','','elements-of-optimization-wheel-350x175','','','2025-10-20 10:46:24','2025-10-20 07:46:24','',1771,'http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/elements-of-optimization-wheel-350x175-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(2881,3,'2025-10-20 10:46:27','2025-10-20 07:46:27','<h2>Marketing Optimization</h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The list of approaches used by the optimizer: </span>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Marketing optimization  В2В</span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In this case marketing is aimed at searching new commercial partners in the business environment. We should warn from the beginning that it is a hard task, since it does not permit subjective representation of the company and its products. This means products and services for business should be represented only from practical point of view. This should be taken into account when drafting text content and distributing links in it.</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Marketing optimization  В2С</span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This task is easier, but at the same time it is connected with substantial share of creativity and requires innovative approach. The company’s products in this case are offered to an average customer who chooses products and services not as a professional, but as an amateur. This means that bare digits are for such amateur are boring and uninformative. You need a catchy text and rich illustrations. </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The goal of the modern commercial website design  is selling services or products. This goal is the main and all online <a href=\"https://web-designservice.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/elements-of-optimization-wheel.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-1245\" src=\"https://web-designservice.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/elements-of-optimization-wheel-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"elements-of-optimization-wheel\" width=\"255\" height=\"255\" /></a>marketing capacities are used to reach this particular goal. Being in the TOP is more important for optimization in B2C scheme. The website targeted at sales to individuals should have higher position (in top three) in search results, bright design and convenient software to make quick purchases “here and now”.  The situation with B2B marketing is slightly different. In this case design heads for back and text content becomes first. Search marketing also looses its positions, because “specialized” websites are rarely created for occasional sales. The </span><b><a href=\"http://rightonit1/\">website marketing</a></b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> heads back, but does not loose its positions. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For example, the main specific of the search optimization for a multipage website of a furniture factory or a metalworks plant is technical specialization where it is more complicated to distribute keywords. In addition, the text should be written for people who visited the website for purpose, and, probably, already have a range of similar offers. Since the sales in this business niche are connected with large amounts of money the competition will be tough. And the first impression from your website will have the major impact on the decision of the potential client. The main difference of the websites marketed in B2B sector is plenty of texts giving full answers on any questions that an average client may have. If the websites targeted at clients that are individuals use graphics as their main weapon, then the websites targeted at companies focus on texts. They should be optimized very carefully avoiding excessive extravagance that may frighten a conservative client. The websites for companies are easier in programming. Usually, it is not needed at all. Purchasing expensive equipment or ordering services from a big enterprise requires long negotiations and collective decision making. That is why no one is hurrying a potential client who represents a company, but at the same time online marketing is made is such a way that the website be easy to find using certain search requests. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Loads of technical terms in the description of the product offered by the company is an important feature of search marketing. There are a lot of such requests, because the offered products and services usually cannot be described briefly and a potential client enters in the search field various words that are more or less associated the item that he is searching for. The more complicated the product offered by the company is, the wider will be the list of keywords from which the semantic kernel of the website will be formed. The psychology of the websites occupying B2C sector is aimed at motivating for immediate purchase. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Comparatively low price of a product or a service, and usability of purchase making are the additional motivation for a visitor. Since a majority of text content on such websites is replaced by graphics the search optimization may be slightly complicated. From other point the search optimization for B2C sector is free from technical terms which significantly facilitate work of optimizer. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Additional convenience when working with B2C websites is the fact that they are usually marketed using famous brand names that gives to the optimizer many opportunities in search marketing, especially if one or another brand appearing on the pages is the its highest popularity points and ensures permanently high demand. Even taking into account high competition among similar websites the marketing will go clock-work! It is more difficult to market special equipment and services without high demand in everyday life, for these reasons the optimizer tries to keep every request. That is why we need the extensive list of keywords mentioned above. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In any case working with both ways of search optimization requires excellent knowledge of search algorithms of the search and indexation of websites by search engines, and not only national search engines, but also foreign ones.</span>\r\n\r\nFill out the form below and we will help you with your Marketing Optimisation\r\n\r\n[caldera_form id=\"CF5591c458259a5\"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Marketing Optimization','','inherit','closed','closed','','1771-revision-v1','','','2025-10-20 10:46:27','2025-10-20 07:46:27','',1771,'http://rightonit1/?p=2881',0,'revision','',0),(2882,3,'2025-10-20 10:47:07','2025-10-20 07:47:07','<h2>SEO why is so important?</h2>\r\nDo you want people to find your website through organic web search?\r\n\r\n... Of course You do... Everyone does want to be in TOP10 Google Organic Search...\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Keyword Research</strong> – Figure out the \"low competitive\" words, highly searched terms in your field of business.  Find out exactly what your clients are looking for.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Analyse your website </strong> – Is it done the right way for proper optimization?  Well... If Your website was developed in Our company - you can skip this step - because the answer is YES. Your website is definitely designed and built RIGHT way and already have <a href=\"http://rightonit1/seo-san-diego/\">basic SEO</a>, Always!</li>