ge downloading speed.</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Directly influences on the behavioral factor. If the website loads slowly the users <a href=\"http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Html-source-code.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-1260\" src=\"http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Html-source-code-261x300.png\" alt=\"Html-source-code\" width=\"261\" height=\"300\" /></a>leave the page not waiting for response.</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The reasons of low speed might be concealed in improper CMS code of the website, in the page overloaded with blocks, in the quality of hosting, and other. </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Micro-markup. </span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> It helps the search engines to process information on the pages of the website to easily provide it in the search results. Such information as address, telephone, working hours and other, if published using special tags then the web crawler will quicker index such information and display it properly in the search results.  </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Generating correct URLs</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Present standards suggest using clean URLs (also known as userflriendly URLs), and absence of duplicates when the URLs are generated automatically.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Using tags.</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Meta tags are used to create headings of the documents, to manage the pages indexation. Meta tags are designated to give the information about the resource pages to the web crawlers therefore proper usage of meta tags on the website is so important. The general meta tags are: title, description, keywords, robots, nofollow.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Canonical URLs.</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> For groups of pages similar in context we specify the preferred (canonical) URL for each page of the group, and this URL will be used in search. The tag &lt;link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"canonical URL of the page\"/&gt; is used for this purpose. </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Creating Sitemap file.</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> This is file containing information about the pages of your website that are subject to index by the search engines. Using Sitemap on the website allows telling the search engine what pages of the resource should be indexed, how often the information on the pages is updated, and what are the most important pages for indexing.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Most web-developers when creating websites do not take into account the requirements of the search engines, unless it is stated in the terms of reference. If you need <a href=\"http://rightonit1/seo-and-organic-search-ranking/\">website SEO</a> , please contact us when drafting terms of reference for programmers. </span>','Optimizing code for SEO marketing','','inherit','closed','closed','','1719-revision-v1','','','2025-10-20 10:50:33','2025-10-20 07:50:33','',1719,'http://rightonit1/?p=2892',0,'revision','',0),(2893,3,'2025-10-20 10:51:02','2025-10-20 07:51:02','','keyword-research-409x204','','inherit','open','closed','','keyword-research-409x204','','','2025-10-20 10:51:02','2025-10-20 07:51:02','',1717,'http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/keyword-research-409x204-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(2894,3,'2025-10-20 10:51:06','2025-10-20 07:51:06','<h2>Keyword research for further web marketing</h2>\r\nCreating the semantic kernel of the website is the basic stage of web marketing.\r\n\r\nWe need to do keyword research to find queries which your potential clients may search. When selecting we proceed from the topic of the website, business tasks and the budget of the project.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Using various services of the search engines, as for example, we receive information regarding monthly frequency of queries (how many people searched for it using the search engine). The higher the frequency of a keyword is the more time, efforts and funds will be needed to improve the website positions in the organic search results. For this reason we usually do not advise our clients to promote high frequency queries, and in average such queries form not <a href=\"http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/keyword-research.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-1257\" src=\"http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/keyword-research-300x137.jpg\" alt=\"keyword-research\" width=\"300\" height=\"137\" /></a>more than 10% of the semantic kernel.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It is more reasonable to stick to the pool of middle frequency and low frequency keyword queries. They have bigger conversion, because they already contain a formed demand, for example, “<a href=\"http://rightonit1/\">web design San Diego</a>”, instead of high frequency query – “web design”. Such queries are much easier to promote what helps to save the budget and get first results quicker. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We always do our best to build the most effective semantic kernel to fit in your budget. In order to do this the goal of the project should be clear. If our main task is to increase the search traffic having limited budget the kernel may be build based on the queries located near to the first page in organic search ranking. Such queries are easier and quicker to promote, plus all necessary landing pages already exist – this helps to reduce costs on their development and content writing . If the main goal is not traffic itself, but the conversion boost, it is also possible to substantially reduce the budget by collecting the queries with the highest conversion based on the website statistics in Google Analytics and to focus solely on promotion of these queries. If you are fighting with your competitors for a share in market we recommend building the semantic kernel based on the queries that let your competitors to be on first pages of organic search, and to work only with this kernel.</span>\r\n\r\nWhat else is very important? Here you will find more answers: <a href=\"http://rightonit1/2016/01/12/the-website-analytics-for-search-promotion/\">website analytics for web marketing</a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When forming the semantic kernel the following moments are considered fundamental: </span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The query should fully comply with the topic of the website.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The general information queries should be excluded.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The queries should be properly formulated.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The queries should be up to date (especially for news websites where content quickly becomes outdated).</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">All aspects of the topic should be covered.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When distributing queries the quantity should not exceed 2-3 queries per one landing page.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Compliance with the website’s structure. </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The frequency and competitiveness of the queries should vary per page. </span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ol>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Forecast</b></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</ol>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When drafting preliminary forecast for keyword research we always proceed from its frequency and competitiveness, current positions of the website for these queries, the technical condition of the website, presence of necessary pages and opportunity to create them. The timeframes for conclusion may change depending on how quickly you implement our recommendations and on frequency of the search engines updates.</span>\r\n<ol>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Distribution</b></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</ol>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The distribution of the collected search queries on the website is equally important. Only 100% correspondence of the landing page to the  visitors query allows receiving high conversion, for this reason we recommend creating special pages for each group of the queries which in many aspects guarantees success of the promotion. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Regardless of the website\'s size  and the volume of the semantic kernel we manually distribute all queries based on the website’s structure. Only by doing so we can guarantee that the landing pages will be relevant to the current queries.  </span>\r\n<ol>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Statistics </b></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</ol>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The statistics regarding positions for all keyword research queries:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">On the day when submitting the commercial offer.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">On the first day when we start promoting the website – to record initial statistics.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Further – every day during all stages of promotion.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The search engines update the statistics on monthly basis, and, having collected the queries today we cannot guarantee that in six months it will give the maximum coverage of the topic. For this purpose we recommend our clients to review the list of queries and to expand it if possible at least once in every six months (in some topics more often). </span>\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Understanding strong and weak sides of the website, and having the pool of the search queries for promotion, we develop </span></i><a href=\"http://rightonit1/2016/01/12/the-website-analytics-for-search-promotion/\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">SEO-strategy</span></i></a><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"http://rightonit1/2016/01/12/the-website-analytics-for-search-promotion/\"> </a>to improve the positions of the website.</span></i>','Keyword research for further web marketing','','inherit','closed','closed','','1717-revision-v1','','','2025-10-20 10:51:06','2025-10-20 07:51:06','',1717,'http://rightonit1/?p=2894',0,'revision','',0),(2895,3,'2025-10-20 10:52:22','2025-10-20 07:52:22','','th-4-300x150','','inherit','open','closed','','th-4-300x150','','','2025-10-20 10:52:22','2025-10-20 07:52:22','',1715,'http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/th-4-300x150-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(2896,3,'2025-10-20 10:52:26','2025-10-20 07:52:26','<h2>The website analytics for web marketing</h2>\r\nThe analytics is the main stage in preparing to the website promotion. Each resource has chances to be promoted in search, and in order to determine the success of your website and to forecast bringing queries to good positions in the search results we need to gather and analyze the website’s general SEO statistics.\r\n<ol>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Website History</b></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</ol>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The age of the domain name is  a great importance for search engines, the older the website the more trust it gets. To young websites  search engines propose to wait, to gain trust and only after to compete for good positions in search results. In addition to the age they take into account the date when the first content was published, as well as the quality and relevance of this content.</span>\r\n\r\nAlso see<a href=\"http://rightonit1/2016/01/12/first-time-web-site-marketing/\"> SEO for young websites</a><a href=\"http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/th-4.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-1253\" src=\"http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/th-4-300x205.jpg\" alt=\"th (4)\" width=\"300\" height=\"205\" /></a>\r\n<ol>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Technical condition</b></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</ol>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The next crucial moment is the current technical condition of the resource. If your website has any duplicates of pages, unoptimized tags, non unique content, pages with no information or with little information, incorrect subdomains and other shortcomings, this will have a negative impact on the website promotion. We hold a quick internal audit of the website which allows us to detect such issues and to determine how much time and efforts we will need for technical optimization of the resource. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Despite a wide algorithmic base applied by the search engines when forming search results and loud statements on cancelling the links,  linkbuilding remains a substantial ranking factor. That is why we need to understand the level and quality of the current links of your website, their dynamics, structure, proportion of new and removed links, anchors. If the website had already been promoted earlier we analyze with regard to unnatural variations of the links or link spam. This information allows estimating the scope of work needed to build the links and to create a proper link strategy to promote your resource. </span>\r\n<ol>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Competitive  website analysis </b></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</ol>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To reach the top positions in the search results your website should outrun the leaders in a number of key figures. To understand what key figures your website needs to improve in comparison with the closest competitors and how much time we be needed to reach them, we hold the competitive analysis, in the course of which we compare the following:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">number of pages in the search engines index;</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">number of external links;</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">number of referrers;</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">approximate search traffic;</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">number of queries in search.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ol>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Counters </b></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</ol>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In 90% of cases we ask you to provide access to the website counters (Google Analytics, and others).This information allows to analyze the volume, character and quantity of the current organic traffic of the resource, to detect conversional queries, to determine basic standard, seasonal activity and other.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After having collected and analyzed this information we can determine whether it is reasonable to promote your website, to draft forecast and to determine the cost. Depending on the size, topic of the resource and set business tasks we determine optimal service plan for promotion based on positions or on the traffic.   </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Brands websites,  niche specialized websites,  small budget websites where content doesn\'t change often (banks, car dealers, websites with closed CMS) ideally fit for position promoting. To the major websites, e-commerce stores or information portals with specialization that includes many brands and models (spare parts for cars, goods for kids), the websites with music and video content, companies supplying wide range services we recommend the traffic promotion. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We need one business day to prepare analytics and the forecast for the website promotion. If we see from the very beginning that there are no chances for promotion then you will receive our response even quicker. The tender offers with full and deep analytics may take up to five business days.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After entering into the agreement and beginning of work we hold additional, more thorough and detailed analysis of your website, based on the results we provide you detailed technical recommendations with regard to SEO that should be implemented on the website.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The analytics is an important stage in the course of the website promotion. That is why after each period we take the statistics and keep track on the changes. You receive all this information in our work reports.</span>\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Having thoroughly analyzed your resource Wise Swan Web Design and deveopment company in San Diego begins selecting the rigt </span></i><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">semantic kernel</span></i><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span></i>\r\n\r\nTo get more information about other principles of SEO visit page <a href=\"http://rightonit1/seo-and-organic-search-ranking/\">SEO and organic search ranking</a>','The website analytics for web marketing','','inherit','closed','closed','','1715-revision-v1','','','2025-10-20 10:52:26','2025-10-20 07:52:26','',1715,'http://rightonit1/?p=2896',0,'revision','',0),(2897,3,'2025-10-20 10:52:43','2025-10-20 07:52:43','','SEO-975x650-974x487','','inherit','open','closed','','seo-975x650-974x487','','','2025-10-20 10:52:43','2025-10-20 07:52:43','',1712,'http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/SEO-975x650-974x487-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(2898,3,'2025-10-20 10:52:45','2025-10-20 07:52:45','<h2>First time web site marketing</h2>\r\nTo create a strategy for such website we need to understand how long the website exists and in what condition are\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/SEO-975x650.jpg\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-1246\" src=\"http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/SEO-975x650-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"SEM industry; SEO company; Internet Marketing Professional; Search SEO Company\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" /></a>\r\n\r\nthe links (if you already have any). Even if the website haв no makketing earlier in the search engines, it still may have external links from context ads or the website content.\r\n\r\nDepending on the age of the website whether it is old or new the  SEO strategies will be totally different. If the website is new the focus will be on low-frequency keywords, if the website is old it is reasonable to try fighting for high-frequency queries.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For websites that are promoted for the first time we do the following:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Analyze current positions and website traffic.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Select keyword queries.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Perform <a href=\"http://rightonit1/2016/01/12/new-website-under-development/\">SEO audit</a>.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Provide SEO recommendations for the website.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Write texts for landing pages.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Check whether the recommendations regarding optimization of the website and its content were published.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Start buying links.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Everyday take results of the website position in keyword queries</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Got Questions?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nGot Questions? We Will Answer!\r\n\r\n[caldera_form id=\"CF566f1dffedc4e\"]','First time web site marketing','','inherit','closed','closed','','1712-revision-v1','','','2025-10-20 10:52:45','2025-10-20 07:52:45','',1712,'http://rightonit1/?p=2898',0,'revision','',0),(2899,3,'2025-10-20 10:53:28','2025-10-20 07:53:28','','SEO1-1240x620 (1)','','inherit','open','closed','','seo1-1240x620-1','','','2025-10-20 10:53:28','2025-10-20 07:53:28','',1710,'http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/SEO1-1240x620-1-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(2900,3,'2025-10-20 10:53:29','2025-10-20 07:53:29','<h2>New website under development</h2>\r\n<strong><em> </em></strong>If you only plan or have just started to develop a website we recommend you involving SEO experts at the initial\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/SEO1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-1242\" src=\"http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/SEO1-300x180.jpg\" alt=\"SEO1\" width=\"300\" height=\"180\" /></a>stage of the web development. This will give you a huge advantage – you will get  already optimized website for search engines with correctly set CMS, correct URLs, optimal structure, and necessary amount of content posted in a right place, etc.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Usually 85%  of just-made websites need additional development to meet the  SEO requirements of the search engines which imply additional expenses. Web-developers create beautiful and good resources, but more often they don’t understand <a href=\"http://rightonit1/2016/01/12/seo-optimization-of-website-structure/\">SEO </a>at all. Our SEO specialists in San Diego will run a number of procedures and draft recommendations which are needed to be implemented in the website that the web crawlers started indexing it straight after launching.  </span>\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What kind of works Wise Swans Web Design and Development can perform:</span></i>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Take all current statistic of the website.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Fix addresses of the webpages being promoted.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Give SEO advice while working on the project.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Advise while creating the structure.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Write texts for landing pages.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After publishing the website on test hosting we fill it with ready-made texts.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hold full SEO check of the website.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Negotiate publishing the website on the general hosting.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Start buying links.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Every day take statistics of the website.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nContact Us Now to get more Information about SEO for new website','New website under development','','inherit','closed','closed','','1710-revision-v1','','','2025-10-20 10:53:29','2025-10-20 07:53:29','',1710,'http://rightonit1/?p=2900',0,'revision','',0),(2901,3,'2025-10-20 10:53:45','2025-10-20 07:53:45','','web-marketing@2x-1500x750','','inherit','open','closed','','web-marketing2x-1500x750','','','2025-10-20 10:53:45','2025-10-20 07:53:45','',1708,'http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/web-marketing@2x-1500x750-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(2902,3,'2025-10-20 10:53:47','2025-10-20 07:53:47','<h2>Strategy of website marketing</h2>\r\nA proper strategy in large part determines success and speed of the website seash marketing. To create a strategy we need to understand what goals and in what timeframes we are trying to meet. In other words SEO strategy is a plan for meeting a certain goal within a set timeframe.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The main goal for promoting the website in the search engines may be: gaining higher positions in the organic search results in a number of significant queries in six months or increasing the search traffic on 10 thousand visits in one year, as well as increasing in two times as many orders from the website in 9 months. It is crucial that the goals be attainable and be in line with the search engines reality and current condition of the website (that\'s why usability is so important). If the goal is formulated incorrectly this might be a waste of time and financial resources, and the result might be never achieved.   </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The strategy is created for each website individually and depends on numerous factors:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Type of the website.</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> An e-commerce store, a content project, a monobrand site and others – each will have its own marketing strategy. </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Topic of the resource. </span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To create the strategy one should understand: how competitive is the topic of the <a href=\"http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/web-marketing@2x.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-1239\" src=\"http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/web-marketing@2x-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"web-marketing@2x\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" /></a>website, what is the size of the search kernel, and is there any seasonal activity, etc.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Age of the website.</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> For example, it is impossible to promote a new website in popular competitive commercial queries.</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In addition it is important to take into account special features of different search engines. For example, at the initial stage Google may be in priority, though it is not the most popular in the Bing, but in Google the first results appear significantly quicker. </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Previous history of the website marketing and development. </span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For example, the website had been rebuilt and pages URLs have been changed, but redirection from old URL to new URL have not been set. This may have negative impact on the website position in the search results and the search traffic. With Wise Swans web design company in San Diego we know how to avoid that!</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Structure of the website.</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Whether it complies with the structure of the search query, whether significant changes are needed. </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Current content of the website .</span></i></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Geography.</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> It is useless to try promoting the website in geo dependent queries in a foreign state. Probably it is necessary to divide the website into different subdomains or different webpages for each website. </span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Taking into account that SEO is a complicated and deep work out of all factors that influence on ranking, our SEO Company will help you  choose the strategy for search promotion based on our hands-on experience. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We are able to write a lot of high quality content for your website, develop technical recommendations to have the web crawler go through all pages, we analyze your traffic, propose ways to increase conversion, place external high quality links , and analyze your competitors. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Depending on the current condition of your website we use different approaches for strategy creation.</span>\r\n\r\nDo you want to know more <a href=\"http://rightonit1/2016/01/12/why-seo-is-so-important/\">Why SEO is so important?</a>\r\n\r\nHave Questions?\r\n\r\nContact Us now\r\n\r\n[caldera_form id=\"CF566f1dffedc4e\"]','Strategy of website marketing','','inherit','closed','closed','','1708-revision-v1','','','2025-10-20 10:53:47','2025-10-20 07:53:47','',1708,'http://rightonit1/?p=2902',0,'revision','',0),(2903,3,'2025-10-20 10:54:03','2025-10-20 07:54:03','<h2>Internal interlinking</h2>\r\nInternal interlinking is an important part of the SEO and organic search ranking which not only allows to offer additional services, goods or content to the user, and thus to increase the average bill, but also helps to redistribute<a href=\"http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/th-3.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-1236\" src=\"http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/th-3-300x184.jpg\" alt=\"th (3)\" width=\"300\" height=\"184\" /></a> the weight in the website and improve behavioral factor.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A well organized interlinking provides an opportunity for the user to go from the page of certain level to the associated category of the same level. In other words when visiting a flypage of an e-commerce store the user should have an opportunity to check out accessories for this item or goods from the other related category.</span>\r\n\r\nThis is not that easy as it seems - so delegate this part to professionals - Wise Swans will help you on every step of SEO\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/seo-optimization-of-website-structure/\">SEO optimization of website structure</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/why-seo-is-so-important/\">Why SEO is so important</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://rightonit1/2016/01/12/links-for-web-promotin/\">Links for the website promotion</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/seo-and-organic-search-ranking/\">SEO and organic search ranking</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nStill got Questions? Feel free to Call US or ask a Question via webform below!\r\n\r\n[caldera_form id=\"CF566f1dffedc4e\"]','Internal interlinking','','inherit','closed','closed','','1706-revision-v1','','','2025-10-20 10:54:03','2025-10-20 07:54:03','',1706,'http://rightonit1/?p=2903',0,'revision','',0),(2904,3,'2025-10-20 10:54:31','2025-10-20 07:54:31','','chart-edited-708x354','','inherit','open','closed','','chart-edited-708x354','','','2025-10-20 10:54:31','2025-10-20 07:54:31','',1704,'http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/chart-edited-708x354-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(2905,3,'2025-10-20 10:54:33','2025-10-20 07:54:33','<h2>SEO optimization of website structure</h2>\r\nA proper structure is 50% of the foundation for a successful website promotion. If the website structure is complicated, illogical and multilayer it is bad for both visitors and the search engines. But that\'s primary a web design issue. To aviod that - visit this page to know more about <a href=\"http://rightonit1/selling-management/\">Web Design usability impovement</a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A web crawler has limited time to go through your website and index it. Our task is to make this procedure effective to the greatest possible extent. That is why first of all we will recommend you introducing userfriendly and well planned containment tree.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We are against creating meaningless pages aimed only at distributing semantic kernel of search queries. In this regard we always come up with options allowing to add missing landing pages in the current website structure and make it look as logical as possible, or to change the website structure hitting requirements of the search engines and user’s logic at the same time. </span>\r\n<ol>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>How the structure is created</b></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</ol>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">First of all we analyze your business and appraise how the current structure can cover the semantic kernel, we <img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-1233\" src=\"http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/chart-edited-300x241.jpg\" alt=\"chart-edited\" width=\"300\" height=\"241\" />compare your website structure with the websites of your closest competitors. We divide the semantic kernel into logical groups based on its characteristics, for example, color, size, category of goods and others, then we find interceptions in these groups. This allows us to determine whether it is enough to add filters to the site or it is necessary to create separate sections for each group of characteristics. Therefore we get the optimized website structure created taking into account the users’ logic and the requirements of search engines.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The  good SEO website structure should:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">be hierarchical, ideally not more than three clicks from the home page;</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">cover the entire semantic kernel in the topic;</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">be logical, concise and userfriendly.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In addition to the navigation structure we recommend using also the following features with regard to the search engines’ requirements: proper addresses of pages, format of internal interlinking of the website, etc.</span>\r\n\r\nIf you need more information about our Web Design and SEO company in San Diego - visit our primary page <a href=\"http://rightonit1/seo-and-organic-search-ranking/\">SEO and organic search </a> or fill out the form below.\r\n\r\n[caldera_form id=\"CF566f1dffedc4e\"]','SEO optimization of website structure','','inherit','closed','closed','','1704-revision-v1','','','2025-10-20 10:54:33','2025-10-20 07:54:33','',1704,'http://rightonit1/?p=2905',0,'revision','',0),(2906,3,'2025-10-20 10:54:49','2025-10-20 07:54:49','','th-2-300x150','','inherit','open','closed','','th-2-300x150','','','2025-10-20 10:54:49','2025-10-20 07:54:49','',1702,'http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/th-2-300x150-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(2907,3,'2025-10-20 10:54:52','2025-10-20 07:54:52','<h2>Links for the website promotion</h2>\r\nWe, as well as the search engines, desire to see in the results only attractive websites of high quality and good usability, completely meeting users’ requirements, and filled with interesting and useful content.\r\n\r\nAnd unlike the search engines we are capable of turning such desires into reality. 80% of our work is concentrated on these factors. The rest 20% is left for working with the website links that are still considered a substantial parameter in website ranking, despite the opinion of the search engines.\r\n\r\nBacklink building is a very important part of <a href=\"http://rightonit1/2016/01/12/why-seo-is-so-important/\">SEO</a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There are several categories of external links:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Natural links</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, that can be gained for proper and interesting content, to which other users or websites’ administrators will be willing to refer, such as articles, photo or video content, blog or forum. Natural links are most valuable foe search engines. </span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Permanent links</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> are bought on special link marketplaces, and if donor platforms were chosen wisely such links look like natural for the search engines. But there is a lot of restrictions so this part should be used very careful.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Links from social networks</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> (Facebook, G+ and others) </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">and quicklinks from Twitter </span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">– made an excellent showing when promoting in topics that need a large number of users to be involved (websites with video or audio content, blogs, information portals). Search engines pay more attention to them than earlier treating them as natural user links. They work quickly and smoothly, because the search engines have a special pool of quickbots that several times a day check social networks. For example, a complete indexation of Twitter links takes only six hours.  </span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThat\'s how Wise Swans Web Design company works:\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">First of all our efforts are concentrated on forming natural links. For this purpose we create ideas to develop your website, we give recommendations regarding content. If there is a need to buy links, we thoroughly select donors, setting the highest requirements. When selecting platforms we take into account its topic, traffic, correlation of inbound and outbound links, and PageRank, percentage of indexed pages, registration in various catalogs, overall <a href=\"http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/th-2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-1230\" src=\"http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/th-2.jpg\" alt=\"th (2)\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a>look of the website, content quantity. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We thoroughly select links for a new website to start promotion from high quality environment. This gives the website a chance to quickly get high positions in Google organic search where requirements to the links are tougher. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If the website has already been promoted it is important to get rid of low quality links history (if any) and to create new links. For this purpose we analyze the links, detect strong and weak spots, as, for example, unstable dynamics, incorrect anchors, donor does not correspond to the topic, etc. If we are not satisfied with the quality of links we replace them with new ones.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">On monthly basis we analyze and check indexation of links, track the state of donor platforms, write anchors. Once in every six months we hold deep and full analysis of links, and based on the results we actualize link strategy of the website.</span>\r\n\r\nIf you want to improve your organic search ranking by getting links - we can help you! It doesn\'t really matter that our SEO company has offices  in Miami, San Diego, San Francisco, Boston and Houston  - we can serve all states, no matter wherу you are located.','Links for the website promotion','','inherit','closed','closed','','1702-revision-v1','','','2025-10-20 10:54:52','2025-10-20 07:54:52','',1702,'http://rightonit1/?p=2907',0,'revision','',0),(2908,3,'2025-10-20 10:55:08','2025-10-20 07:55:08','','th-1-238x119','','inherit','open','closed','','th-1-238x119','','','2025-10-20 10:55:08','2025-10-20 07:55:08','',1700,'http://rightonit1/wp-content/uploads/2016/